    <!-- Customer Panel -->
    <script>
    function initCustomerPanel() {
        return {
            open: false,
            activeTab: '',
            openCustomerPanel: function(event) {
                let newActiveTab = event.detail.activeTab;

                /* This event is dispatched here even if it's also the case in toggleActiveTab, otherwise we can't
                properly catch it for our needs. Indeed, the open-customer-panel event is fired at the same time. */
                if (this.activeTab !== newActiveTab) {
                    window.dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('active-tab-changed', {
                        detail: {
                            activeTab: newActiveTab
                        }
                    }));
                }

                this.activeTab = newActiveTab;
                this.open = !this.open;

                Alpine.store('bodyOverflow').disableOverflow();
            },
            closeModal: function() {
                this.open = false;
                Alpine.store('bodyOverflow').enableOverflow();
                window.dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('close-customer-panel'));
            },
            toggleActiveTab: function(tabName) {
                if (this.activeTab !== tabName) {
                    window.dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('active-tab-changed', {
                        detail: {
                            activeTab: tabName
                        }
                    }));
                }

                this.activeTab = tabName;
            }
        }
    }
</script>
<aside id="customer-panel"
       x-data="initCustomerPanel()"
       x-cloak
       @open-customer-panel.window="openCustomerPanel($event)"
       @keydown.window.escape="closeModal()"
>
    <div role="dialog"
         aria-label="customer-panel"
         aria-modal="true"
         class="fixed inset-y-0 right-0 z-30 flex h-svh">
        <div class="backdrop"
             x-show="open"
             x-transition:enter="ease-in-out duration-500"
             x-transition:enter-start="opacity-0"
             x-transition:enter-end="opacity-100"
             x-transition:leave="ease-in-out duration-500"
             x-transition:leave-start="opacity-100"
             x-transition:leave-end="opacity-0"
             @click="closeModal()"
             aria-label="Close panel"></div>
        <div class="relative w-full"
             x-show="open"
             x-transition:enter="transform transition ease-in-out duration-500 sm:duration-700"
             x-transition:enter-start="translate-x-full"
             x-transition:enter-end="translate-x-0"
             x-transition:leave="transform transition ease-in-out duration-500 sm:duration-700"
             x-transition:leave-start="translate-x-0"
             x-transition:leave-end="translate-x-full"
        >
            <div class="h-full grid grid-rows-[theme(height.16)_1fr] w-screen-10 md:w-screen-1/2 lg:w-screen-3/4 xl:w-screen-1/2
                    bg-white text-primary text-sm leading-tight"
            >
                                <header class="flex justify-between px-4 items-center border-b">
                    <div class="flex gap-x-8 h-full">
                                                                                    <p
                                class="flex items-center uppercase text-sm font-normal cursor-pointer transition duration-300
                                border-b-2 border-transparent"
                                :class="{'border-secondary-darkest font-bold': activeTab === 'Account', 'border-transparent font-normal': activeTab !== 'Account'}"
                                @click="toggleActiveTab('Account')"
                                >
                                Account                                </p>
                                                                                                                <p
                                class="flex items-center uppercase text-sm font-normal cursor-pointer transition duration-300
                                border-b-2 border-transparent"
                                :class="{'border-secondary-darkest font-bold': activeTab === 'Cart', 'border-transparent font-normal': activeTab !== 'Cart'}"
                                @click="toggleActiveTab('Cart')"
                                >
                                Cart                                </p>
                                                                        </div>
                    <button @click="closeModal()"
                            class="btn-close ml-2"
                            aria-label="Close panel">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" role="img">
<path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M12 12.7071L17.3033 18.0104L18.0104 17.3033L12.7071 12L18.0104 6.6967L17.3033 5.98959L12 11.2929L6.69669 5.98959L5.98959 6.69669L11.2929 12L5.98958 17.3033L6.69669 18.0104L12 12.7071Z" fill="#202020"/>

                                        <input name="referer" type="hidden" value="aHR0cHM6Ly9tYWlzb25raXRzdW5lLmNvbS93dy9zcGVlZHktZm94LXBhdGNoLWNvbWZvcnQtc3dlYXRzaGlydC1ibGFjay02NTgxOTBlZTVlODY2Lmh0bWw~">
                                    </div>

                <div>
                    <template x-if="displayErrorMessage">
                        <p class="text-red flex items-center">
                            <span class="inline-block w-8 h-8 mr-3">
                                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" width="24" height="24" role="img">

        <script>
    function initMagicLinkForm() {
        return {
            open: false,
            message: '',
            error: false,
            errors: 0,
            submitForm() {
                // Do not rename $form, the variable is expected to be declared in the recaptcha output
                const $form = document.querySelector('#magic\u002Dlogin\u002Dlink\u002Dform');
                    if (!this.hasCaptchaToken) {
        this.errors = 1;


        const executeGreCaptcha = () => {
            grecaptcha.ready(() => {
                grecaptcha.execute(
                    '6LdD\u002D6MqAAAAAHpZwzNhPnLjh_IH9_GBdDcBYX7X',
                    {action: 'submit'}
                ).then((token) => {
                    if (token && token.length > 0) {
                        $form['g\u002Drecaptcha\u002Dresponse'].value = token;
                        this.errors = 0;
                        this.hasCaptchaToken = 1;
                        (this.submitForm || $form.submit).call(this);
                    } else {
                        this.errors = 1;
                        const error = 'ReCaptcha\u0020validation\u0020failed,\u0020please\u0020try\u0020again';
                        if (this.setErrorMessages) {
                            this.setErrorMessages([error])
                            this.displayErrorMessage = true;
                        } else {
                            window.dispatchMessages && window.dispatchMessages([{type: "error", text: error}], 5000);
                        }
                    }
                }).catch(exception => {
                    console.error(exception || `An unknown error occurred during ReCaptcha validation. Are the tokens and the domain correctly set up in the Google console?`)
                });
            })
        }

        if (window.grecaptcha) {
            executeGreCaptcha();
        } else {
            const recaptchaUrl = "https://www.google.com/recaptcha/api.js?render=6LdD\u002D6MqAAAAAHpZwzNhPnLjh_IH9_GBdDcBYX7X";
            const script = document.createElement('script');
            script.setAttribute('type', 'text/javascript');
            script.setAttribute('src', recaptchaUrl);
            document.head.appendChild(script);

            script.addEventListener("load", executeGreCaptcha, false);
        }
    }
                    if (this.errors === 0) {
                    fetch($form.action, {
                        method: 'POST',
                        body: new URLSearchParams(new FormData($form)),
                        headers: {
                            'Content-Type': 'application/x-www-form-urlencoded;charset=UTF-8',
                            'X-Requested-With': 'XMLHttpRequest'
                        }
                    }).then(response => {
                        if (response.ok) {
                            this.message = 'If this email address is associated with an account, you will receive an email with a link to log in.';
                        } else {
                            this.message = 'An error occurred, please try again later';
                            this.error = true;
                        }
                    })
                }
            }
        }
    }
</script>

        function initCustomerLoginForm() {
            return {
                errors: 0,
                hasCaptchaToken: 0,
                displayErrorMessage: false,
                errorMessages: [],
                setErrorMessages(messages) {
                    this.errorMessages = [messages]
                    this.displayErrorMessage = this.errorMessages.length
                },
                submitForm() {
                    // do not rename $form, the variable is the expected name in the recaptcha output
                    const $form = document.querySelector('#customer-login-form');
                    
                    if (this.errors === 0) {
                        $form.submit();
                    }
                }
            }
        }

                            <script>
    function initCartDrawer() {
        return {
            isLoading: false,
            forceAuthentication: false,
            formKey: hyva.getFormKey(),
            cart: {},
            maxItemsToDisplay: 10,
            itemsCount: 0,
            totalCartAmount: 0,
            isLoggedIn: false,
            isGlobalEEnabled: true,
            checkoutUrl: 'https://maisonkitsune.com/ww/checkout',
            promoRules: [{"attribute":"qty","operator":">=","message_before":"","message_after":"","value":"2"}],
            promoMessages: [],
            proceedToCheckoutLabel: 'Proceed to Checkout',
            getData(data) {
                if (data.cart) {
                    this.cart = data.cart;
                    this.itemsCount = data.cart.items && data.cart.items.length || 0;
                    this.totalCartAmount = this.cart.summary_count;
                    this.forceAuthentication = !data.cart.isGuestCheckoutAllowed;
                    this.setCartItems();
                    this.setProceedToCheckoutLabel(data);
                }
                this.isLoading = false;
                this.isLoggedIn = data.customer && data.customer.firstname;
                this.setCheckoutUrl();
                this.setPromoMessage();
            },
            cartItems: [],
            setProceedToCheckoutLabel(data) {
                if (!data?.cart?.preorder) {
                    this.proceedToCheckoutLabel = 'Proceed to Checkout'
                    return;
                }

                this.proceedToCheckoutLabel = 'Pre-order'
            },
            getItemCountTitle() {
                return hyva.strf('(%0 of %1)', this.maxItemsToDisplay, this.itemsCount)
            },
            setCartItems() {
                this.cartItems = this.cart.items && this.cart.items.sort((a, b) => b.item_id - a.item_id) || [];

                if (this.maxItemsToDisplay > 0) {
                    this.cartItems = this.cartItems.slice(0, parseInt(this.maxItemsToDisplay, 10));
                }
            },
            setCheckoutUrl() {
                if (!this.isGlobalEEnabled) {
                    this.checkoutUrl = 'https://maisonkitsune.com/ww/checkout';
                    return;
                }

                this.checkoutUrl = !this.isLoggedIn ? 'https://maisonkitsune.com/ww/international/login' :
                    'https://maisonkitsune.com/ww/international/checkout'

            },
            setPromoMessage() {
                let subtotal = this.cart.subtotalAmount;
                let subtotalWithoutDiscount = this.cart.subtotalAmountWithoutDiscount;
                let diff = 0;
                let diffMessage = '';

                this.promoMessages = [];

                if (typeof (subtotal) !== 'undefined' && subtotal === null) {
                    subtotal = 0;
                }

                if (typeof (subtotalWithoutDiscount) !== 'undefined' && subtotalWithoutDiscount === null) {
                    subtotalWithoutDiscount = 0;
                }

                if (this.promoRules.length !== 0) {
                    let isRuleWithoutDiscount = this.checkRule(this.promoRules);
                    if(isRuleWithoutDiscount){
                        subtotal = subtotalWithoutDiscount;
                    }
                    if (typeof (subtotal) !== 'undefined') {
                        diff = this.getMinRule(subtotal);
                    }
                }

                if (diff && Object.keys(diff).length && ((subtotal !== 0 && diff['value'] > 0) || subtotal === 0)) {
                    //Add currency symbol
                    diffMessage = hyva.formatPrice(diff['amount']);
                    if (diff['message_before'] !== '') {
                        this.promoMessages.push(diff['message_before'].replace('%1', diffMessage));
                    }
                } else {
                    //Else if have a free gift, show message_after
                    this.promoRules.forEach((rule) => {
                        if (rule && rule['message_after'] !== '') {
                            this.promoMessages.push(rule['message_after'].replace('%1', diffMessage));
                        }
                    })
                }
            },
            checkRule(rules) {
                return rules.find((rule) => rule['attribute'] === 'subtotal_without_discount_items');
            },
            getMinRule(subtotal) {
                let diff = [];
                this.promoRules.forEach(function (rule) {
                    if ((parseFloat(subtotal) <= parseFloat(rule.value) && rule.operator === '>') ||
                        (parseFloat(subtotal) < parseFloat(rule.value) && rule.operator === '>=') &&
                        ((typeof (rule.max) !== 'undefined' && parseFloat(subtotal) < parseFloat(rule.max)) || typeof (rule.max) === 'undefined')) {
                        diff = rule;
                        diff['amount'] = rule.value - subtotal;
                        return diff;
                    }
                });
                return diff;
            },
            deleteItemFromCart(itemId) {
                this.isLoading = true;

                const removeUrl = BASE_URL + 'checkout/sidebar/removeItem/';

                fetch(removeUrl, {
                    "headers": {
                        "content-type": "application/x-www-form-urlencoded; charset=UTF-8",
                    },
                    "body": `form_key=${this.formKey}&item_id=${itemId}`,
                    "method": "POST",
                    "mode": "cors",
                    "credentials": "include"
                }).then(response => {
                    if (response.redirected) {
                        window.location.href = response.url;
                    } else if (response.ok) {
                        return response.json();
                    } else {
                        window.dispatchMessages && window.dispatchMessages([{
                            type: 'warning',
                            text: 'Could\u0020not\u0020remove\u0020item\u0020from\u0020quote.'
                        }]);
                        this.isLoading = false;
                    }
                }).then(result => {
                    window.dispatchMessages && window.dispatchMessages([{
                        type: result.success ? 'success' : 'error',
                        text: result.success
                            ? 'You\u0020removed\u0020the\u0020item.'
                            : result.error_message
                    }], result.success ? 2000 : 0);

                    if (result.success) {
                        this.trackingUpdateCart('remove_from_cart', itemId);
                    }
                    window.dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('reload-customer-section-data'));
                });
            },
            updateQty(code, qty, itemId) {
                if (code === 'dec' && qty === 1) {
                    this.deleteItemFromCart(itemId)
                }

                this.isLoading = true;
                const updateUrl = BASE_URL + 'checkout/sidebar/updateItemQty/';
                const updatedQty = code === 'inc' ? qty + 1 : qty - 1;

                fetch(updateUrl, {
                    "headers": {
                        "content-type": "application/x-www-form-urlencoded; charset=UTF-8",
                    },
                    "body": `item_id=${itemId}&item_qty=${updatedQty}&form_key=${this.formKey}`,
                    "method": "POST",
                    "mode": "cors",
                    "credentials": "include"
                }).then(response => {
                    if (response.redirected) {
                        window.location.href = response.url;
                    } else if (response.ok) {
                        switch (code) {
                            case 'inc':
                                this.trackingUpdateCart('add_to_cart', itemId);
                                break;
                            case 'dec':
                                this.trackingUpdateCart('remove_from_cart', itemId);
                                break;
                        }

                        return response.json();
                    } else {
                        window.dispatchMessages && window.dispatchMessages([{
                            type: 'warning',
                            text: 'Could\u0020not\u0020update\u0020item'
                        }]);
                        this.isLoading = false;
                    }
                }).then(() => {
                    window.dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('reload-customer-section-data'));
                });
            },
            resolveItemVariant(option, color) {
                if (!option) {
                    return;
                }

                return color ?
                    `${option[0]?.value}::${color.name?.toLowerCase()}` :
                    `${option[0]?.value}`;
            },
            resolveItems() {
                let items = [];
                const cartItems = this.cart.items;
                Object.keys(cartItems).map((productKey) => items.push(
                    this.resolveItemData(cartItems[productKey]))
                );

                return items;
            },
            resolveProductById(productId) {
                return this.cart.items.find(item =>
                    item.item_id === productId
                );
            },
            resolveItemData(product) {
                if (!product) {
                    return {};
                }

                return {
                    item_id: product.product_sku ?? '',
                    item_name: product.product_name?.toLowerCase() ?? '',
                    affiliation: '',
                    coupon: '',
                    currency: window?.algoliaConfig?.currencyCode ?? '',
                    item_category: product.tracking?.item_category ?? '',
                    item_category2: product.tracking?.item_category2 ?? '',
                    item_category3: product.tracking?.item_category3 ?? '',
                    item_category4: product.tracking?.item_category4 ?? '',
                    item_category5: product.tracking?.item_category5 ?? '',
                    discount: this.resolveItemDiscount(product),
                    index: 0,
                    item_brand: Alpine.store('currentUniverse') ?? '',
                    item_list_id: '',
                    item_list_name: '',
                    item_variant: this.resolveItemVariant(product.options, product.product_color) ?? '',
                    price: parseFloat(product.product_price_value) ?? 0,
                    quantity: 1
                };
            },
            resolveItemDiscount(product) {
                return parseFloat(product.basedPriceValue ?
                    product.basedPriceValue - product.product_price_value
                    : 0
                );
            },
            resolveItemAddedLocation(item) {
                item['added_location'] = 'cart';
                return item;
            },
            trackingUpdateCart(actionName, itemId) {
                mhTracking.pushEcommerce(
                    actionName,
                    actionName === 'add_to_cart' ?
                        [
                            this.resolveItemAddedLocation(this.resolveItemData(this.resolveProductById(itemId)))
                        ] : [
                            this.resolveItemData(this.resolveProductById(itemId))
                        ]
                )
            },
            openCart() {
                this.open = true;
                Alpine.store('bodyOverflow').disableOverflow();
            },
            closeCart() {
                this.open = false;
                Alpine.store('bodyOverflow').enableOverflow();
            }
        }
    }
</script>
<div id="cart-drawer"
     class="cart-drawer h-full"
     x-data="initCartDrawer()"
     @private-content-loaded.window="getData($event.detail.data)"
>
    <template x-if="cart">
        <div class="flex flex-col w-screen-10 md:w-screen-1/2 lg:w-screen-3/4 xl:w-screen-1/2 h-full
                    bg-white text-primary text-sm leading-tight"
             @click.outside="$dispatch('tracking-toggle-cart')"
        >
                        <template x-for="promoMessage in promoMessages">
                <div x-html="promoMessage"
                     class="px-8 py-2 bg-secondary-lighter text-base text-secondary text-center "></div>
            </template>
            <template x-if="!promoMessages.length">
                <div></div>
            </template>

            
            <div class="p-4 pb-0 mb-4 overflow-y-auto">
                <template x-for="item in cartItems">
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-[93px_1fr] gap-4 border-b border-dark-lighter">
                        <template x-if="!item.am_free_message && !item.free_sample && item.product_type !== 'giftbox'">
                            <a :href="item.product_url"
                               class="border-0 relative"

    x-data="initMinicartCrosssell()"

<!-- Algolia product selection scripts -->

<script>
    if (typeof productSelectionConfigMinicart == "undefined") {
        function loadScript(url) {
            let script = document.createElement('script')
            script.setAttribute('type', 'text/javascript')
            script.setAttribute('src', url)
            document.head.append(script)

            return new Promise((resolve) => script.addEventListener('load', resolve))
        }

        function loadScripts(scripts) {
            window.algoliaLoading = true;
            return Promise.all(scripts.map(loadScript))
        }

        function getScriptsToLoad(productSelectionScripts) {
            const scripts = document.scripts;
            return productSelectionScripts.filter((algoliaScript) => {
                const scriptsContainingAlgolia = Array.from(scripts).filter((script) => {
                    if (!script.src) {
                        return false;
                    }

                    return script.src.includes(algoliaScript);
                })

                return !scriptsContainingAlgolia.length
            });
        }

        function loadScriptCallbackMinicart(productSelectionConfigMinicart ) {
            if (!window.algolia) {
                initAlgoliaCommon()
            }

            if (!window.algoliaAnalytics && typeof initInsights === 'function') {
                initInsights();
            }
            initAlgoliaProductSelectionForMinicart(productSelectionConfigMinicart );
        }

        function initProductSelectionMinicart() {
            const productSelectionConfigMinicart =
                {
                    "page": "minicart",
                    "suffix_index_name": "_products_ordered_qty_desc",
                    "container": "#minicart_crosssell_products",
                    "nb_hits": "4",
                    "algolia_event_name": "minicart",
                    "filters": {"facets":{"categoryIds":["13974","13975","13976","13977","13978"]},"numericRefinements":{"price.EUR.group_0":{"<=":[150],">":[25]},"in_stock":{"=":[1]},"preorder":{"!=":[1]},"uniq_size":{"=":[1]}}}                };
            const productSelectionScripts = ["https:\/\/static.maisonkitsune.com\/static\/version1749733577\/frontend\/MaisonHyva\/default\/en_US\/Hyva_AlgoliaSearch\/js\/internals\/instantsearch.production.min.js","https:\/\/static.maisonkitsune.com\/static\/version1749733577\/frontend\/MaisonHyva\/default\/en_US\/Hyva_AlgoliaSearch\/js\/common.js","https:\/\/static.maisonkitsune.com\/static\/version1749733577\/frontend\/MaisonHyva\/default\/en_US\/Hyva_AlgoliaSearch\/js\/internals\/search-insights.min.js","https:\/\/static.maisonkitsune.com\/static\/version1749733577\/frontend\/MaisonHyva\/default\/en_US\/Hyva_AlgoliaSearch\/js\/internals\/algoliasearch-lite.js"];
            const scriptsToLoad = getScriptsToLoad(productSelectionScripts);

            if (scriptsToLoad.length) {
                loadScripts(scriptsToLoad).then(() => {
                    window.algoliaLoading = false;
                    if (!window.algoliaLoadingInclude && !window.algoliaLoadingRecommend) {
                        if (window.algoliaScriptsToLoadInstant) {
                            window.algoliaScriptsToLoadInstant.forEach((script) => script());
                            window.algoliaScriptsToLoadInstant = [];
                        }

                        if (window.algoliaScriptsToLoadRecommend) {
                            window.algoliaScriptsToLoadRecommend.forEach((script) => script());
                            window.algoliaScriptsToLoadRecommend = [];
                        }

                        if (document.getElementById("crosssell-hit-template") !== null) {
                            if (window.algoliaScriptsToLoad) {
                                window.algoliaScriptsToLoad.forEach((script) => script());
                                window.algoliaScriptsToLoad = [];
                            }

                            loadScriptCallbackMinicart(productSelectionConfigMinicart);
                        } else {
                            window.algoliaScriptsToLoad = window.algoliaScriptsToLoad ? window.algoliaScriptsToLoad : [];
                            window.algoliaScriptsToLoad.push(loadScriptCallbackMinicart.bind(this, productSelectionConfigMinicart));
                        }
                    } else {
                        window.algoliaScriptsToLoad = window.algoliaScriptsToLoad ? window.algoliaScriptsToLoad : [];
                        window.algoliaScriptsToLoad.push(loadScriptCallbackMinicart.bind(this, productSelectionConfigMinicart));
                    }
                });
            } else {
                const isAlgogoLoading = window.algoliaLoading || window.algoliaLoadingInclude || window.algoliaLoadingRecommend;
                const isHitTemplateLoading = document.getElementById("crosssell-hit-template") === null;
                if (isAlgogoLoading || isHitTemplateLoading) {
                    window.algoliaScriptsToLoad = window.algoliaScriptsToLoad ? window.algoliaScriptsToLoad : [];
                    window.algoliaScriptsToLoad.push(loadScriptCallbackMinicart.bind(this, productSelectionConfigMinicart));
                } else {
                    loadScriptCallbackMinicart(productSelectionConfigMinicart);
                }
            }
        }

        function initAlgoliaProductSelectionForMinicart(productSelectionConfigMinicart ) {
            /** Redeclare filters which are already in productSelectionConfig, because Algolia seems to override these
            latters each time we use them in transformItems **/
            const filters = {"facets":{"categoryIds":["13974","13975","13976","13977","13978"]},"numericRefinements":{"price.EUR.group_0":{"<=":[150],">":[25]},"in_stock":{"=":[1]},"preorder":{"!=":[1]},"uniq_size":{"=":[1]}}};

            const ctx = 'minicart';
            forceLoadSplide();
            selectors = {
                relatedTitle: '.product-related-tabs__content .title',
                algoliaResult: '.algolia-instant-selector-results',
                algoliaResultWrapper: '.algolia-instant-results-wrapper'
            };

            const searchClient = algoliasearch(algoliaConfig.applicationId, algoliaConfig.apiKey);
            const ruleContexts = ['magento_filters', ''];
            const originPage = productSelectionConfigMinicart .page;

            ruleContexts.push('magento-landingpage-' + originPage);
            const format = window.isMobile() ? 'mobile' : 'desktop';

            let defaultFilters = productSelectionConfigMinicart.filters.facets;

            const instantsearchOptions = {
                searchClient: searchClient,
                indexName: algoliaConfig.indexName + productSelectionConfigMinicart.suffix_index_name,
                searchFunction: function (helper) {
                    if (productSelectionConfigMinicart.filters) {
                        if (productSelectionConfigMinicart.filters.numericRefinements) {
                            helper.state.numericRefinements = {
                                ...helper.state.numericRefinements,
                                ...productSelectionConfigMinicart.filters.numericRefinements
                            }
                        }

                        if (defaultFilters) {
                            for (const [key, value] of Object.entries(defaultFilters)) {
                                if ((helper.state.disjunctiveFacetsRefinements[key] && !helper.state.disjunctiveFacetsRefinements[key].length) || typeof (helper.state.disjunctiveFacetsRefinements[key]) === "undefined") {
                                    helper.state.disjunctiveFacetsRefinements[key] = value;
                                }
                            }
                        }
                    }
                    helper.search();
                }
            }

            const searchParameters = {
                hitsPerPage: productSelectionConfigMinicart.nb_hits,
                ruleContexts: ruleContexts,
                clickAnalytics: true,
                analyticsTags: [originPage, format],
                query: ''
            };

            const search = instantsearch(instantsearchOptions);

            search.addWidgets([
                instantsearch.widgets.hits(addHits()),
                instantsearch.widgets.configure(searchParameters),
            ]);

            const productSelectionMiddleWare = instantsearch.middlewares.createInsightsMiddleware({
                onEvent: (event) => {
                    const {insightsMethod, payload, widgetType, eventType} = event;
                    const query = search.helper.lastResults.query;

                    if (widgetType === 'ais.hits' && eventType === 'view') {
                        window.dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent(`product-selection-init-${ctx}`, {detail: {event}}));
                    }
                }
            });

            search.use(productSelectionMiddleWare);
            search.start();

            function addHits() {
                return {
                    container: productSelectionConfigMinicart.container,
                    templates: {
                        empty: '',
                        item: document.getElementById("crosssell-hit-template").innerHTML
                    },
                    cssClasses: {
                        root: ["splide__track"],
                        list: ["splide__list"],
                        item: ["splide__slide"]                    },
                    transformItems: function (items) {
                        
                        if (filters && filters?.facets?.objectID) {
                            items.sort((a, b) => filters.facets.objectID.indexOf(a.objectID) - filters.facets.objectID.indexOf(b.objectID));
                        }

                        return items.map(function (item) {
                            item.__indexName = search.helper.lastResults.index;
                            item = transformHit(item, algoliaConfig.priceKey, search.helper);
                            item.eventName = productSelectionConfigMinicart.algolia_event_name;
                            item.lazy_splide = true;
                            return item;
                        });
                    }
                };
            }
        }

        function forceLoadSplide() {
            if (!window.AlpineJSLoadedAlgolia && typeof Alpine !== 'undefined') {
                Alpine.store('hyva_splide_js').forceLoad();
                window.AlpineJSLoadedAlgolia = true;
            }
        }

        // Condition for the Algolia minicart crossell, because this template is generic
                    // Optimization to trigger Algolia queries only when we open the crossell's tab
            if (!maisonHyva.isStringEmpty(sessionStorage.getItem('minicartSlider'))) {
                Alpine.store('minicartAlgoliaTriggered', true);
            }

            window.addEventListener('active-tab-changed', event => {
                if (event.detail.activeTab === 'Cart' && Alpine.store('minicartAlgoliaTriggered') !== true) {
                    initProductSelectionMinicart();
                    Alpine.store('minicartAlgoliaTriggered', true);
                }
            });
            }
</script>

<script>
    function initMinicartCrosssell() {
        return {
            isSliderMounted: false,
            sliderId: 'minicart_crosssell_products',
            sliderKey: 'minicartSlider',
            /* As we need to force Splide loading in initSplider and at the same time have an x-effect in order to
            prevent Splide loading errors, this variable allows us to not call x-effect if not desired */
            initSpliderCalled: false,
            isAllowed: false,
            getCartData(data) {
                this.isAllowed = !data.cart?.preorder;
            },
            mountSlider() {
                new Splide(`#${this.sliderId}`, {
                    type: 'slide',
                    perMove: 1,
                    arrows: false,
                    pagination: true,
                    drag: true,
                    fixedWidth: 'min(500px, 100%)',
                    gap: '16px',
                    breakpoints: {
                        1024: {
                            fixedWidth: 'min(286px, 100%)',
                        }
                    }
                }).mount();
            },
            isSplideLoaded() {
                return Alpine.store('hyva_splide_js').is_loaded;
            },
            canMountSlider(event) {
                return document.getElementById(this.sliderId) &&
                    this.isSplideLoaded() &&
                    !this.isSliderMounted &&
                    event &&
                    event.detail.activeTab === 'Cart';
            },
            initSplider(forceSplideLoading = false, event = null) {
                this.initSpliderCalled = true;

                if (!this.isSplideLoaded() && forceSplideLoading) {
                    Alpine.store('hyva_splide_js').forceLoad();
                }

                /* setTimeout to take account of Splide time loading and DOM changes. Parent panel is in display none
                and has no width, so we let a little time for the panel to have one. And then we can build our slider
                avoiding the bug of pagination not being visible. */
                setTimeout(() => {
                    if (!this.canMountSlider(event)) {
                        return;
                    }

                    const storedSlider = sessionStorage.getItem(this.sliderKey);

                    if (!maisonHyva.isStringEmpty(storedSlider)) {
                        document.getElementById(this.sliderId).innerHTML = storedSlider;

                        this.mountSlider();
                    } else {
                        sessionStorage.setItem(this.sliderKey, document.getElementById(this.sliderId).innerHTML);

                        this.mountSlider();
                    }

                    this.isSliderMounted = true;
                }, 1000);
            }
        }
    }
</script>
            </div>
                                    <template x-if="cart.summary_count">
                <div class="mt-auto p-4 flex max-md:flex-col gap-4 border-t-2 border-secondary-lighter">
                    <a href="https://maisonkitsune.com/ww/checkout/cart"
                       :title="proceedToCheckoutLabel"
                       class="btn btn-primary w-full flex justify-between w-full"
                    >
                        <span x-html="proceedToCheckoutLabel"></span>
                        <span class="subtotal">
                                    <span class="amount price-container">
                                        <span x-html="cart.subtotal" class="price-wrapper"></span>
                                    </span>
                                </span>
                    </a>
                                    </div>
            </template>
                    </div>
</div>

     left-1/2 top-1/2 bg-secondary-darkest/70 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2"

<script>
    'use strict';

    function initScrollListener() {
        return {
            open: true,
            show: true,
            prevScrollVal: window.scrollY,
            immersiveClasses: null,
            immersiveEnabled: true,
            headerBottom: null,
            init() {
                this.retrieveImmersiveClass();
                this.toggleImmersiveClass();
                this.headerObserver();
            },
            headerObserver() {
                const header = document.querySelector('#header');

                if (!header) {
                    return;
                }

                const resizeObserver = new ResizeObserver(() => {
                    this.setHeaderHeight();
                });

                resizeObserver.observe(header);

                const  mutationObserver = new MutationObserver((mutationList) => {
                    for (let mutation of mutationList) {
                        if (mutation.type === 'childList') {
                            this.setHeaderHeight();
                        }
                    }
                });

                mutationObserver.observe(header, {childList: true, subtree: true});
            },
            setHeaderHeight() {
                setTimeout(() => {
                    const headerBottom = document.querySelector('#header').getBoundingClientRect().bottom;

                    document.documentElement.style.setProperty('--header-height', `${headerBottom}px`);

                    if (headerBottom > this.headerBottom) {
                        document.documentElement.style.setProperty('--max-header-height', `${headerBottom}px`);
                    }

                    this.headerBottom = headerBottom;
                }, 200);
            },
            handleScroll() {
                this.setHeaderHeight();
            },
            handleMenuOpen() {
                if (!Alpine.store('isMobile')) {
                    return;
                }
                this.open = !this.open;
            },
            mobileBehavior() {
                if (Alpine.store('isMobile')) {
                    return;
                }
                this.open = true;
                Alpine.store('bodyOverflow').enableOverflow();
            },
            retrieveImmersiveClass() {
                const immersiveClass = [...document.body.classList]
                    .filter((className) => className.includes('immersive-'))
                    .join();
                this.immersiveClasses = immersiveClass.length ? immersiveClass : null;
            },
            toggleImmersive(state) {
                if (!state) {
                    this.manuallyToggleImmersiveClass(!state);
                }
                this.immersiveEnabled = state;
                if (state) {
                    this.manuallyToggleImmersiveClass(!state);
                }
            },
            toggleImmersiveClass() {
                if (!this.immersiveClasses) {
                    return;
                }

                if (!this.immersiveEnabled) {
                    return;
                }

                if (window.scrollY) {
                    document.body.classList.remove(this.immersiveClasses);
                } else {
                    document.body.classList.add(this.immersiveClasses);
                }
            },
            manuallyToggleImmersiveClass(disable = true) {
                if (!this.immersiveClasses) {
                    return;
                }

                if (!this.immersiveEnabled) {
                    return;
                }

                if (disable) {
                    document.body.classList.remove(this.immersiveClasses);
                } else if (!disable && !window.scrollY) {
                    document.body.classList.add(this.immersiveClasses);
                }
            }
        }
    }
</script>
</header><main id="maincontent" class="page-main"><div x-data="initHeaderSearchResult()"
     x-defer="interact"
     @open-customer-panel.window="isCartOpen=true"
     @close-customer-panel.window="isCartOpen=false"
     @scroll.throttle="dispatchScroll()"
     class="header-instant-container hidden top-[var(--header-height)] left-0 right-0 fixed h-main overflow-y-scroll pb-4 bg-white"
     :class="isCartOpen ? 'z-[25]' : 'z-30 delay-700'"
     @tracking-toggle-cart.window="trackingCartPopIn()"
>
</div>
<script>
    function initHeaderSearchResult() {
        return {
            isCartOpen: false,
            trackingCartPopIn() {
                mhTracking.pushDataLayer({
                    event: 'popin_cart',
                    action: this.isCartOpen ? 'open_popin'
                        : 'close_popin'
                });
            },
            dispatchScroll() {
                if (!Alpine.store('isMobile')) {
                    return;
                }

                window.dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('search-mobile-scroll'));
            }
        }
    }
</script>
<div id="algolia-autocomplete-container"></div><div id="contentarea" tabindex="-1"></div>
<div class="page messages"><script>
        window.defaultSuccessMessageTimeout = 2000;
        function initMessages() {
        "use strict";
        return {
            messages: window.mageMessages || [],
            isEmpty() {
                return this.messages.reduce(
                    function (isEmpty, message) {
                        return isEmpty && message === undefined
                    }, true
                )
            },
            removeMessage(messageIndex) {
                this.messages[messageIndex] = undefined;
            },
            addMessages(messages, hideAfter) {
                messages.map((message) => {
                    this.messages = this.messages.concat(message);
                    if (hideAfter === undefined && message.type !== 'error'  && window.defaultSuccessMessageTimeout) {
                        hideAfter = window.defaultSuccessMessageTimeout;
                    }
                    if (hideAfter) {
                        this.setHideTimeOut(this.messages.length -1, hideAfter);
                    }
                });
            },
            setHideTimeOut(messageIndex, hideAfter) {
                setTimeout((messageIndex) => {
                    this.removeMessage(messageIndex);
                }, hideAfter, messageIndex);
            },
            getIcon(context) {
                let iconHtml;
                switch (context) {
                                    case 'cart':
                        iconHtml = "<svg xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" fill=\"none\" class=\"fill-current\" role=\"img\">\n<g id=\"icon\/cart_4\">\n<path id=\"Union_9\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M10 6V8H11V6H13V13C13 13.5523 12.5523 14 12 14H4C3.44772 14 3 13.5523 3 13V6H5V8H6V6H10ZM11 5H13H14V6V13C14 14.1046 13.1046 15 12 15H4C2.89543 15 2 14.1046 2 13V6V5H3H5V3C5 1.34315 6.34315 0 8 0C9.65685 0 11 1.34315 11 3V5ZM6 5V3C6 1.89543 6.89543 1 8 1C9.10457 1 10 1.89543 10 3V5H6Z\" fill=\"#202020\"\/>\n<\/g>\n<title>shopping-bag<\/title><\/svg>\n";
                        break;
                    case 'wishlist':
                        iconHtml = "<svg xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" role=\"img\">\n<path d=\"M11.6464 6.52511L12 6.87867L12.3535 6.52511L13.0606 5.81801C14.818 4.06065 17.6672 4.06065 19.4246 5.81801C21.1819 7.57537 21.1819 10.4246 19.4246 12.182L12 19.6066L4.57534 12.182C2.81798 10.4246 2.81798 7.57537 4.57534 5.81801C6.3327 4.06065 9.18195 4.06065 10.9393 5.81801L11.6464 6.52511Z\" stroke=\"#202020\"\/>\n<title>heart<\/title><\/svg>\n";
                        break;
                    default :
                        iconHtml = "<svg xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" fill=\"currentColor\" class=\"fill-current\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" role=\"img\">\n  <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M18 10a8 8 0 11-16 0 8 8 0 0116 0zm-7-4a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zM9 9a1 1 0 000 2v3a1 1 0 001 1h1a1 1 0 100-2v-3a1 1 0 00-1-1H9z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"\/>\n<title>information-circle<\/title><\/svg>\n";
                    // phpcs:enable Generic.Files.LineLength.TooLong
                }
                return iconHtml;
            },

            getColor(messageType, property, contrary) {
                let color;
                switch (messageType) {
                    case 'success':
                        color = !contrary ? `${property}-green-darker` : 'primary';
                        break;
                    case 'error':
                        color = !contrary ? `${property}-red-darker` : 'primary';
                        break;
                    case 'info':
                        color = !contrary ? `${property}-blue-darker` : 'primary';
                        break;
                    default:
                        color = !contrary ? `${property}-blue-darker` : 'primary';
                }
                return color;
            },
            eventListeners: {
                ['@messages-loaded.window']() {
                    this.addMessages(event.detail.messages, event.detail.hideAfter)
                },
                ['@private-content-loaded.window'](event) {
                    const data = event.detail.data;
                    if (
                        data.messages &&
                        data.messages.messages &&
                        data.messages.messages.length
                    ) {
                        this.addMessages(data.messages.messages);
                    }
                },
                ['@clear-messages.window']() {
                    this.messages = [];
                }
            }
        }
    }
</script>
<section x-data="initMessages()"
         x-bind="eventListeners"
>
    <div role="alert" class="max-w-80 md:max-w-[680px] mx-auto">
        <template x-for="(message, index) in messages" :key="index">

<script>
    function initDeferredAddToCart() {
        return {
            isLoadingButton: false,
            isSelectedOptionEnable: {},

            currentFinalPrice: '',
            currentOldPrice: '',

            areAllSelectedOptionsEnabled() {
                return Object.values(this.isSelectedOptionEnable).every(
                    (option) => option
                );
            },

            eventListeners: {
                ['@swatch-options-data-update.window'](event) {
                    const attributeCode = event.detail.attributeCode;

                    this.isSelectedOptionEnable = {
                        ...this.isSelectedOptionEnable,
                        [attributeCode]: event.detail.isOptionEnable
                    };
                },
                ['@product-addtocart-started.window'](event) {
                    this.isLoadingButton = true;
                },
                ['@product-addtocart-complete.window'](event) {
                    this.isLoadingButton = false;
                },
                ['@update-prices-94258.window'](event) {
                    this.currentFinalPrice = event.detail.finalPrice.amount;
                    this.currentOldPrice = event.detail.oldPrice.amount;
                }
            }
        }
    }
</script>
    </form>
    <div
        class="absolute top-4 right-4 cursor-pointer"
        @click="hide"
    >
        <span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" role="img">
<path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M12 12.7071L17.3033 18.0104L18.0104 17.3033L12.7071 12L18.0104 6.6967L17.3033 5.98959L12 11.2929L6.69669 5.98959L5.98959 6.69669L11.2929 12L5.98958 17.3033L6.69669 18.0104L12 12.7071Z" fill="#202020"/>
<title>x</title></svg>
</span>
    </div>
</div>
<script>
    function initAddToCartModal() {
        return {
            allOptions: {},
            disabledOptions: {},
            selectedOption: {},
            resolveItemData() {
                return {
                    item_id: 'MM00313KM0307-P199',
                    item_name: `speedy fox patch comfort sweatshirt`,
                    affiliation: '',
                    coupon: '',
                    currency: window?.algoliaConfig?.currencyCode ?? '',
                    item_category: `men`,
                    item_category2: `ready to wear`,
                    item_category3: `sweatshirt`,
                    item_category4: `collection`,
                    item_category5: ``,
                    discount: this.resolveItemDiscount(),
                    index: 0,
                    item_brand: Alpine.store('currentUniverse') ?? '',
                    item_list_id: '',
                    item_list_name: '',
                    price: this.resolveItemPrice(),
                    item_variant: '',
                    quantity: 1,
                    page_url: 'https://maisonkitsune.com/ww/speedy-fox-patch-comfort-sweatshirt-black-658190ee5e866.html'
                };
            },
            resolveItemDiscount() {
                return 0;
            },
            resolveItemStockStatus(item) {
                item['stock_status'] = 'in_stock';
                return item;
            },
            resolveItemPrice() {
                return 190;
            },
            resolveItemAddedLocation(item) {
                item['added_location'] = 'pdp';
                return item;
            },
            resolveItemVariant(item) {
                item['item_variant'] = `${this.selectedOption.mk_size ?? ''}::`
                    + `black`;
                return item;
            },
            trackingViewItem() {
                mhTracking.pushEcommerce(
                    'view_item',
                    [
                        this.resolveItemStockStatus(this.resolveItemData())
                    ]
                );
            },
            trackingAddToCart() {
                mhTracking.pushEcommerce(
                    'add_to_cart',
                    [
                        this.resolveItemVariant(this.resolveItemAddedLocation(this.resolveItemData()))
                    ]
                );
            },
            dispatchSwatchOptionsUpdate() {
                const optionLabel = this.selectedOption.mk_size;
                const optionId = this.allOptions.mk_size.find((element) => element.label === optionLabel).id;
                const isOptionEnable = !this.disabledOptions.mk_size.find((element) => element.label === optionLabel);
                const attributeCode = 'mk_size';

                window.dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('swatch-options-data-update', {
                    detail: {
                        isOptionEnable,
                        attributeCode,
                        optionLabel,
                        optionId
                    }
                }));
            },
            handleSubmit(event) {
                event.preventDefault();

                if (!this.selectedOption.mk_size) {
                    return;
                }

                window.dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('add-to-cart-deferred', {}));
            },

            eventListeners: {
                ['@swatch-options-data-init.window'](event) {
                    this.allOptions = event.detail.allOptions;
                    this.disabledOptions = event.detail.disabledOptions;
                },
                ['@swatch-options-data-update.window'](event) {
                    const attributeCode = event.detail.attributeCode;

                    this.selectedOption = {
                        ...this.selectedOption,
                        [attributeCode]: event.detail.optionLabel
                    };
                },
                ['@add-to-cart-deferred-complete.window'](event) {
                    this.trackingAddToCart();

                    if (!this.opened['add-to-cart-modal']) {
                        return;
                    }

                    this.hide('add-to-cart-modal', event.detail.event);
                }
            }
        }
    }
</script>
        </div>
    </div>
    </div>

                            </span>

                            <span

                                x-html="hyva.formatPrice(currentFinalPrice)"></span>

<script>
    function initDeferredAddToCart() {
        return {
            isLoadingButton: false,
            isSelectedOptionEnable: {},

            currentFinalPrice: '',
            currentOldPrice: '',

            areAllSelectedOptionsEnabled() {
                return Object.values(this.isSelectedOptionEnable).every(
                    (option) => option
                );
            },

            eventListeners: {
                ['@swatch-options-data-update.window'](event) {
                    const attributeCode = event.detail.attributeCode;

                    this.isSelectedOptionEnable = {
                        ...this.isSelectedOptionEnable,
                        [attributeCode]: event.detail.isOptionEnable
                    };
                },
                ['@product-addtocart-started.window'](event) {
                    this.isLoadingButton = true;
                },
                ['@product-addtocart-complete.window'](event) {
                    this.isLoadingButton = false;
                },
                ['@update-prices-75900.window'](event) {
                    this.currentFinalPrice = event.detail.finalPrice.amount;
                    this.currentOldPrice = event.detail.oldPrice.amount;
                }
            }
        }
    }

<script>
    function initStickyATB() {
        return {
            isVisible: false,

            initIsAddToCartVisible() {
                const element = document.querySelector('#product-addtocart-button');
                const header = document.querySelector('#header');

                const checkVisibility = () => {
                    const rect = element.getBoundingClientRect();
                    if (rect.bottom >= header.offsetHeight) {
                        if (this.isVisible) {
                            this.isVisible = false;
                        }
                    } else {
                        if (!this.isVisible) {
                            this.isVisible = true;
                        }
                    }
                };

                window.addEventListener('scroll', checkVisibility);
                window.addEventListener('resize', checkVisibility);
                window.addEventListener('load', checkVisibility);
            }
        }
    }

    function initStickyATBForm() {
        return {
            allOptions: {},
            disabledOptions : {},
            selectedOption: {},

            dispatchSwatchOptionsUpdate() {
                const optionLabel = this.selectedOption.mk_size;
                const optionId = this.allOptions.mk_size.find((element) => element.label === optionLabel).id;
                const isOptionEnable = !this.disabledOptions.mk_size.find((element) => element.label === optionLabel);
                const attributeCode = 'mk_size';

                window.dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('swatch-options-data-update', {
                    detail: {
                        isOptionEnable,
                        attributeCode,
                        optionLabel,
                        optionId
                    }
                }));
            },
            handleSubmit(event) {
                event.preventDefault();

                this.validate()
                    .then(() => {
                        if (window.screen.width < 1024) {
                            this.show('add-to-cart-modal', event);
                            return;
                        }

                        window.dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('add-to-cart-deferred', {}));
                    })
                    .catch((invalid) => {
                        if (invalid.length > 0) {
                            invalid[0].focus();
                        }
                    });
            },

            eventListeners: {
                ['@swatch-options-data-init.window'](event) {
                    this.allOptions = event.detail.allOptions;
                    this.disabledOptions = event.detail.disabledOptions;

                    if (this.allOptions.mk_size.length === 1) {
                        this.selectedOption.mk_size = this.allOptions.mk_size[0].label;
                    }
                },
                ['@swatch-options-data-update.window'](event) {
                    const attributeCode = event.detail.attributeCode;

                    this.selectedOption = {
                        ...this.selectedOption,
                        [attributeCode]: event.detail.optionLabel
                    };
                },
            }
        }
    }
</script>

<script>
    function initWannaVTO() {
        return {
            open: false,
            wannaFullUrl: null,
            wannaUrl: ''.replaceAll('&amp;', '&'),
            mobileUrlParams: '&mode=vto&experience=vto',
            desktopUrlParams: '&mode=3d',
            init() {
                this.setWannaUrl();
            },
            setWannaUrl() {
                this.wannaFullUrl = Alpine.store('isMobile')
                    ? `${this.wannaUrl}${this.mobileUrlParams}`
                    : `${this.wannaUrl}${this.desktopUrlParams}`;
            },
            openWanna() {
                this.open = true;
                Alpine.store('bodyOverflow').disableOverflow();
                window.scrollTo(0,0);
            },
            closeWanna(preventMobile = false) {
                if (preventMobile && Alpine.store('isMobile')) {
                    return;
                }

                this.open = false;
                Alpine.store('bodyOverflow').enableOverflow();
            }
        }
    }
</script>

        <script>
    function initPrice75900() {

                const regularPriceInclTaxKey = 'oldPrice',
            regularPriceExclTaxKey = 'baseOldPrice',
            finalPriceInclTaxKey = 'finalPrice',
            finalPriceExclTaxKey = 'basePrice';

        function calculateCustomOptionPrices(activeCustomOptions, customOptionPrices) {
            return activeCustomOptions.reduce((priceAccumulator, activeCustomOptionId) => {
                const customOptionPrice = customOptionPrices[activeCustomOptionId];
                if (customOptionPrice) {
                    return Number.parseFloat(priceAccumulator) + Number.parseFloat(customOptionPrice);
                }
                return priceAccumulator;
            }, 0);
        }

        return {
            regularPriceKey: regularPriceInclTaxKey,
            finalPriceKey: finalPriceInclTaxKey,
            activeProductsPriceData: false,
            initialFinalPrice: 190,
            calculatedFinalPrice: false,
            calculatedFinalPriceWithCustomOptions: false,
            initialTierPrices: [],
            showRegularPriceLabel: false,
            customOptionPrices: [],
                        activeCustomOptions: [],
            qty: 1,
            updateCustomOptionActive(data) {
                let activeCustomOptions = this.activeCustomOptions;
                const customOptionId = data.customOptionId;

                if (data.active) {
                    if (!activeCustomOptions.includes(customOptionId)) {
                        activeCustomOptions.push(data.customOptionId);
                    }
                } else {
                    if (customOptionId && activeCustomOptions.includes(customOptionId)) {
                        let index = activeCustomOptions.indexOf(customOptionId);
                        activeCustomOptions.splice(index, 1);
                    }
                }
                this.calculateFinalPriceWithCustomOptions()
            },
            updateCustomOptionPrices(prices, basePrices) {
                if (prices) {
                    this.customOptionPrices = prices;
                }

                
                this.calculateFinalPriceWithCustomOptions();
            },
            calculateFinalPrice() {

                const findApplicableTierPrice = (initialPrice, withTax) => {
                    if (this.activeProductsPriceData && this.activeProductsPriceData.tierPrices) {
                        const key = withTax ? 'price' : 'basePrice'
                        return this.activeProductsPriceData.tierPrices.reduce((acc, tierPrice) => {
                            if (this.qty >= tierPrice.qty && tierPrice[key] < acc) {
                                return tierPrice[key];
                            }
                            return acc;
                        }, this.activeProductsPriceData[withTax ? finalPriceInclTaxKey : finalPriceExclTaxKey].amount);

                    } else {
                        const key = withTax ? 'price_incl_tax' : 'price_excl_tax';
                        return Object.values(this.initialTierPrices).reduce((acc, tierPrice) => {
                            if (this.qty >= tierPrice.price_qty && tierPrice[key] < acc) {
                                return tierPrice[key];
                            }
                            return acc;
                        }, initialPrice);

                    }
                }

                this.calculatedFinalPrice = findApplicableTierPrice(this.initialFinalPrice, true);
                window.dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent("update-product-final-price", {detail: this.calculatedFinalPrice}));

                            },
            calculatePriceLabelVisibility() {
                this.showRegularPriceLabel =
                    (this.calculatedFinalPrice === this.activeProductsPriceData[this.regularPriceKey].amount) &&
                    this.activeProductsPriceData.isMinimalPrice;
            },
            calculateFinalPriceWithCustomOptions() {
                const finalPrice = this.calculatedFinalPrice || this.initialFinalPrice;
                this.calculatedFinalPriceWithCustomOptions = finalPrice + this.getCustomOptionPrice();
                            },
            getCustomOptionPrice() {
                return calculateCustomOptionPrices(this.activeCustomOptions, this.customOptionPrices);
            },
                        getFormattedFinalPrice() {
                return hyva.formatPrice(
                    this.calculatedFinalPriceWithCustomOptions ||
                    this.calculatedFinalPrice ||
                    this.initialFinalPrice
                )
            },
                        isPriceHidden() {
                const finalPrice = this.calculatedFinalPriceWithCustomOptions ||
                    this.calculatedFinalPrice ||
                    this.initialFinalPrice;
                return false && finalPrice === 0;
            },
            eventListeners: {
                ['@update-prices-75900.window'](event) {
                    this.activeProductsPriceData = event.detail;

                    this.calculateFinalPrice();
                    this.calculateFinalPriceWithCustomOptions();
                    this.calculatePriceLabelVisibility();
                },
                ['@update-qty-75900.window'](event) {
                    this.qty = event.detail;
                    this.calculateFinalPrice();
                    this.calculateFinalPriceWithCustomOptions();
                },
                ['@update-custom-option-active.window'](event) {
                    this.updateCustomOptionActive(event.detail);
                },
                ['@update-custom-option-prices.window'](event) {
                    this.updateCustomOptionPrices(event.detail);
                },
                            }
        }
    }
</script>
<div
    x-data="initPrice75900()"
    x-bind="eventListeners"
    class="price-box price-final_price flex py-2 lg:justify-end lg:items-end lg:py-3"
>
    <template x-if="!activeProductsPriceData && !isPriceHidden()">
        <div class="price-container">
            <div>
                <span
                    id="product-price-75900"
                    class="price-wrapper text-primary text-sm leading-normal font-bold uppercase"
                    :class="{'text-red': ''}"
                    product-vat="20"
                                              data-fp='[]'
                                     >
                    <span class="price" x-html="getFormattedFinalPrice()">
                        <span class="price" data-ignore="true">€190.00</span>                    </span>
                </span>
            </div>

                    </div>
    </template>
    <template x-if="activeProductsPriceData">
        <div class="price-container">
            <div class="final-price inline-block">
                <span
                    id="product-price-75900"
                    class="price-wrapper text-primary text-sm leading-normal font-bold uppercase"
                    product-vat="20"
                                              data-fp='[]'
                                         :class="{
                        'text-red': activeProductsPriceData.oldPrice &&
                        activeProductsPriceData[finalPriceKey].amount < activeProductsPriceData[regularPriceKey].amount
                    }"
                >
                    <span class="price !visible" x-html="getFormattedFinalPrice()"></span>
                </span>
            </div>
            <template x-if="activeProductsPriceData.oldPrice &&
            activeProductsPriceData[finalPriceKey].amount < activeProductsPriceData[regularPriceKey].amount">
                <div class="old-price flex">
                    <span
                        id="product-price-75900"
                        class="price-wrapper"
                        product-vat="20"
                                              data-fp='[]'
                                         >
                        <span
                            class="price !visible text-primary text-[11px] leading-normal font-bold line-through uppercase"
                            x-html="hyva.formatPrice(activeProductsPriceData[regularPriceKey].amount + getCustomOptionPrice())"
                        ></span>
                    </span>
                </div>
            </template>
        </div>
    </template>
</div>

<script>
    function initOutOfStockModal() {
        return {
            email: '',
            errors: 0,
            is_subscribed_email: false,

            init() {
                this.initEmail();
            },
            submitForm() {
                this.validate()
                    .then(() => {
                        this.isLoading = true;
                        // Do not rename $form, the variable is expected to be declared in the recaptcha output
                        const $form = document.querySelector('#stock\u002Dalert\u002Dproduct');
                            if (!this.hasCaptchaToken) {
        this.errors = 1;


        const executeGreCaptcha = () => {
            grecaptcha.ready(() => {
                grecaptcha.execute(
                    '6LdD\u002D6MqAAAAAHpZwzNhPnLjh_IH9_GBdDcBYX7X',
                    {action: 'submit'}
                ).then((token) => {
                    if (token && token.length > 0) {
                        $form['g\u002Drecaptcha\u002Dresponse'].value = token;
                        this.errors = 0;
                        this.hasCaptchaToken = 1;
                        (this.submitForm || $form.submit).call(this);
                    } else {
                        this.errors = 1;
                        const error = 'ReCaptcha\u0020validation\u0020failed,\u0020please\u0020try\u0020again';
                        if (this.setErrorMessages) {
                            this.setErrorMessages([error])
                            this.displayErrorMessage = true;
                        } else {
                            window.dispatchMessages && window.dispatchMessages([{type: "error", text: error}], 5000);
                        }
                    }
                }).catch(exception => {
                    console.error(exception || `An unknown error occurred during ReCaptcha validation. Are the tokens and the domain correctly set up in the Google console?`)
                });
            })
        }

        if (window.grecaptcha) {
            executeGreCaptcha();
        } else {
            const recaptchaUrl = "https://www.google.com/recaptcha/api.js?render=6LdD\u002D6MqAAAAAHpZwzNhPnLjh_IH9_GBdDcBYX7X";
            const script = document.createElement('script');
            script.setAttribute('type', 'text/javascript');
            script.setAttribute('src', recaptchaUrl);
            document.head.appendChild(script);

            script.addEventListener("load", executeGreCaptcha, false);
        }
    }
                            if (this.errors === 0) {
                            this.ajaxProductAlert($form);
                        }
                    })
                    .catch((invalid) => {
                        if (invalid.length > 0) {
                            invalid[0].focus();
                        }
                    });
            },
            ajaxProductAlert(form) {
                const url = BASE_URL + 'productalert/add/stock';

                const parameters = {
                    'form_key': hyva.getFormKey(),
                    'product_id': '75900',
                    'option_id': this.getOptionIdFromOptionLabel(this.selectedOption.mk_size).shift().id,
                    'email': this.email,
                    'g-recaptcha-response': form.elements['g-recaptcha-response'].value                };

                if (this.is_subscribed_email) {
                    parameters.is_subscribed_email = true;
                }

                fetch(url, {
                    method: "POST",
                    headers: {
                        "Content-Type": "application/x-www-form-urlencoded; charset=UTF-8",
                        Accept: "application/json",
                    },
                    body: new URLSearchParams(parameters),
                })
                    .then((result) => {
                        if (result.ok) {
                            return result.json();
                        }
                    })
                    .then((data) => {
                        this.hide(); // call hide method from parent modal
                        this.email = '';
                        this.isLoading = false;
                        window.dispatchMessages(
                            [{
                                type: data.success ? "success" : "error",
                                text: data.message
                            }], 5000
                        );

                        if (data.error_nl) {
                            window.dispatchMessages(
                                [{
                                    type: 'warning',
                                    text: data.error_nl
                                }], 5000
                            );

                            return;
                        }

                        mhTracking.pushNewsletterEvent(
                            'subscribe_newsletter_from_back_in_stock',
                            1
                        );
                    })
                    .catch((data) => {
                        window.dispatchMessages(
                            [{
                                type: "error",
                                text: data.message
                            }], 5000
                        )
                    });
            },

            getCustomerData(data) {
                if (data.customer && data.customer.email) {
                    this.email = data.customer.email;
                }
            },
            getOptionIdFromOptionLabel(selectedSizeLabel) {
                return this.disabledOptions.mk_size
                    .filter((size) => size.label === selectedSizeLabel);
            },
            eventListeners: {
                ['@fill-oos-email.window'](event) {
                    if (event.detail.email) {
                        this.email = event.detail.email;
                    }
                }
            },
            initEmail() {
                window.dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('get-oos-email'));
            }
        }
    }
</script>
        </div>
    </div>
    </div>
            </div>
        </template>

<script>
    function initAddToCart() {
        return {
            isLoading: false,
            isLoadingButton: false,
            isRestricted: false,
            isSelectedOptionEnable: {},
            selectedOption: [],
            disabledOptions: {},
            restrictedCountries: [],
            email: '',
            selectedSize: '',

            init() {
                this.initIsRestricted();
            },
            areAllSelectedOptionsEnabled() {
                return Object.values(this.isSelectedOptionEnable).every(
                    (option) => option
                );
            },
            outOfStockClick(event) {
                this.show('out-of-stock-modal', event);
            },
            initIsRestricted() {
                const cookie = hyva.getCookie('GlobalE_Data');
                try {
                    let countryValue = JSON.parse(decodeURIComponent(cookie));
                    this.isRestricted = this.restrictedCountries.includes(countryValue?.countryISO);
                } catch {
                    this.isRestricted = false;
                }
            },

            eventListeners: {
                ['@swatch-options-data-init.window'](event) {
                    this.disabledOptions = event.detail.disabledOptions;
                },
                ['@swatch-options-data-update.window'](event) {
                    const attributeCode = event.detail.attributeCode;

                    this.selectedSize = event.detail.optionLabel;

                    this.selectedOption = {
                        ...this.selectedOption,
                        [attributeCode]: event.detail.optionLabel
                    }
                    this.isSelectedOptionEnable = {
                        ...this.isSelectedOptionEnable,
                        [attributeCode]: event.detail.isOptionEnable
                    };
                },
                ['@product-addtocart-started.window'](event) {
                    this.isLoadingButton = true;
                },
                ['@product-addtocart-complete.window'](event) {
                    this.isLoadingButton = false;

                    window.dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('product-addtocart-complete-callback', {
                        detail: {
                            productSku: 'MM00313KM0307-P199',
                            productSize: this.selectedSize
                        }
                    }));
                },
                ['@get-oos-email.window']() {
                    const _self = this;
                    window.dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('fill-oos-email', {
                        detail: {
                            email: _self.email
                        }
                    }));
                }
            },
            getCustomerData(data) {
                if (data.customer && data.customer.email) {
                    this.email = data.customer.email;
                }
            }
        }
    }
</script>
        </div>

<script>
    function initColors() {
        return {
            formatColorName(colorName) {
                const firstChar = colorName.charAt(0);
                const restColorName = colorName.substring(1);

                return firstChar.toUpperCase() + restColorName.toLowerCase();
            },
        }
    }
</script>
