            const swatchOptionsComponent = initSwatchOptions(
                {"263":{"103":{"type":"0","value":"XS","label":"XS"},"101":{"type":"0","value":"S","label":"S"},"100":{"type":"0","value":"M","label":"M"},"99":{"type":"0","value":"L","label":"L"},"102":{"type":"0","value":"XL","label":"XL"},"104":{"type":"0","value":"XXL","label":"XXL"},"additional_data":"{\"update_product_preview_image\":1,\"use_product_image_for_swatch\":0,\"swatch_input_type\":\"text\"}"}}            );

            function dispatchSwatchOptionsUpdate(isOptionEnable, attributeId, optionLabel) {
                const attributeCode = this.optionConfig.attributes[attributeId].code;

                window.dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('swatch-options-data-update', {
                    detail: {
                        isCoreEvent: true,
                        isOptionEnable,
                        attributeCode,
                        optionLabel
                    }
                }))
            }

            function initDispatchSwatchOptions() {
                const attributeIds = Object.values(this.optionConfig.attributes).reduce((res, current) => {
                    res[current.code] = current.code;
                    return res;
                }, {});
                const allOptions = Object.values(this.optionConfig.attributes).reduce((res, current) => {
                    res[current.code] = current.options;
                    return res;
                }, {});
                const disabledOptions = Object.values(this.optionConfig.attributes).reduce((res, current) => {
                    res[current.code] = _getDisabledOptions(this.optionConfig, current.id);
                    return res;
                }, {});

                window.dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('swatch-options-data-init', {
                    detail: {
                        disabledOptions: disabledOptions,
                        allOptions: allOptions,
                        attributeIds: attributeIds
                    }
                }));
            }

            function _getDisabledOptions(optionConfig, attributeId) {
                return optionConfig.attributes[attributeId].options.filter((option) => {
                    if (option.products.length <= 0) {
                        return option;
                    }
                });
            }

            function fitleGetAllAvailableSizes() {
                let customAvailableSizes = this.allowedAttributeOptions.filter((option) =>
                    option.length
                );
                customAvailableSizes = customAvailableSizes[0]?.map((size) => size.label);
                return customAvailableSizes ? customAvailableSizes.join(',') : '';
            }

            return Object.assign(
                configurableOptionsComponent,
                {
                    ...swatchOptionsComponent,
                    dispatchSwatchOptionsUpdate,
                    initDispatchSwatchOptions,
                    fitleGetAllAvailableSizes
                },
                {
                    init() {
                        this.initShowSwatchesIntersect();
                        this.initDispatchSwatchOptions();
                        this.findAllowedAttributeOptions();
                        this.updatePrices();
                    }
                }
            );
        }
    </script>

<script>
    function initAddToCartForm() {
        return {
            eventListeners: {
                ['@add-to-cart-submit-product.window'](event) {
                    const form = event.detail.form;
                    this.doSubmitRequest(form);
                }
            },
            ajaxSubmit(event, form) {
                event.preventDefault();
                window.dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('product-addtocart-started'));
                                    const ctx = 'product';
                        window.dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('add-to-cart-preorder-modal', {detail: {form, ctx}}));
                                    },
            doSubmitRequest(form) {
                const formData = new FormData(form);

                const fitleTrackId = maisonHyva.getFitleTrackId();
                if (fitleTrackId.length > 0) {
                    formData.append('fitle_track_id', fitleTrackId);
                }

                //Hack to add objectid
                const url = new URL(window.location.href);
                const queryID = url.searchParams.get("queryID");
                if (queryID) {
                    formData.append('queryID', queryID);
                }

                fetch(form.action, {
                    method: 'POST',
                    body: new URLSearchParams(formData),
                    headers: {
                        'Content-Type': 'application/x-www-form-urlencoded;charset=UTF-8',
                        'X-Requested-With': 'XMLHttpRequest'
                    }
                })
                    .then((res) => {
                        if (!res.ok) {
                            form.submit();
                        }

                        return res.json();
                    })
                    .then((data) => {
                        if (data.backUrl) {
                            form.submit();
                        }
                        window.dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('product-addtocart-success'));
                        window.dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('reload-customer-section-data'));
                    })
                    .catch((error) => {
                        window.dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('product-addtocart-error'));

                        this.setMessage({
                            text: 'There was a problem adding your item to the cart.',
                            type: 'error'
                        });
                    })
                    .finally(() => {
                        window.dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('product-addtocart-complete'));
                        window.dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('add-to-cart-deferred-complete', {detail: {event}}));
                    });
            },
            setMessage(message) {
                if (typeof window.dispatchMessages !== "undefined") {
                    window.dispatchMessages(
                        [message], 2000
                    );
                }
            }
        }
    }
</script>
    </div>

    
<div class="hidden justify-between items-center has-*:mt-2 has-*:flex">

width=\"87\">12<\/td>\r\n<td class=\"xl67\" width=\"87\">30<\/td>\r\n<td class=\"xl66\" width=\"87\">30<\/td>\r\n<td class=\"xl66\" width=\"87\">11.8110\"<\/td>\r\n<\/tr>\r\n<\/tbody>\r\n<\/table>\r\n<table>\r\n<thead>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\" colspan=\"8\"><strong>HAVAIANAS<\/strong><\/td>\r\n<\/tr>\r\n<\/thead>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Cent. (cm)<\/strong><\/td>\r\n<td>23cm<\/td>\r\n<td>24\/25cm<\/td>\r\n<td>25\/26cm<\/td>\r\n<td>27cm<\/td>\r\n<td>28cm<\/td>\r\n<td>29cm<\/td>\r\n<td>31cm<\/td>\r\n<\/tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>EU<\/strong><\/td>\r\n<td>35\/36<\/td>\r\n<td>37\/38<\/td>\r\n<td>39\/40<\/td>\r\n<td>41\/42<\/td>\r\n<td>43\/44<\/td>\r\n<td>45\/46<\/td>\r\n<td>47\/48<\/td>\r\n<\/tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>UK<\/strong><\/td>\r\n<td>3\/4<\/td>\r\n<td>4,5\/5<\/td>\r\n<td>6\/7<\/td>\r\n<td>7,5\/8<\/td>\r\n<td>9\/10<\/td>\r\n<td>11\/12<\/td>\r\n<td>13<\/td>\r\n<\/tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Taille recommand\u00e9e Havaianas<\/strong><\/td>\r\n<td>35\/36<\/td>\r\n<td>37\/38<\/td>\r\n<td>39\/40<\/td>\r\n<td>41\/42<\/td>\r\n<td>43\/44<\/td>\r\n<td>45\/46<\/td>\r\n<td>47\/48<\/td>\r\n<\/tr>\r\n<\/tbody>\r\n<\/table>\r\n<\/div>"},
            count: 0,
            activeTab: null,
            isTabEnable: false,
            sliderPosition: 0,
            sliderWidth: 0,
            init() {
                this.count = Object.keys(this.sizeGuides).length;
                this.isTabEnable = this.count > 1;
                this.activeTab = Object.keys(this.sizeGuides)[0];
                this.sliderWidth = `${100/this.count}%`;

            },
            changeActiveTab(activeTab) {
                if (!activeTab){ return }
                this.activeTab = activeTab;

                if (this.count === 0) { return }
                const index = Object.keys(this.sizeGuides).indexOf(activeTab) ?? 0;
                const leftPercentage = ( 100/this.count ) * index;
                this.sliderPosition = `${leftPercentage}%`;
            }
        }
    }
</script>
<div x-data="initSizeGuide()" x-defer="interact" class="size-guide-container">
    <template x-if="isTabEnable">
        <div>
            <div class="sticky top-0 flex bg-container text-lg text-center border-2 border-secondary-darker">
                <template x-for="(guide, index) in sizeGuides">
                    <span x-text="index" @click="changeActiveTab(index)"  class="block flex-1 py-4 cursor-pointer"></span>
                </template>
                <span class="block absolute top-0 h-full w-1/2 bg-primary mix-blend-difference pointer-events-none
                    transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out"
                    :style="{left: sliderPosition, width: sliderWidth}"
                ></span>
            </div>
            <template x-for="(guide, index) in sizeGuides">
                <div x-html="guide" x-show="activeTab === index"></div>
            </template>
        </div>
    </template>
    <template x-if="!isTabEnable">
        <template x-for="guide in sizeGuides">
            <div x-html="guide"></div>
        </template>
    </template>
</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
    </aside>
</div>




                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </template>
    <template x-if="!$store.isMobile">
        <div
            :class="{'hidden' : !isTabVisible }"
        >
            <div class="max-w-screen-xl break-words text-sm text-primary-lighter py-4">
                <script>
    function initSizeGuidePanel() {
        return {
            open: false,
            openModal: function () {
                this.open = !this.open;
                Alpine.store('bodyOverflow').disableOverflow();
            },
            closeModal: function () {
                this.open = false;
                Alpine.store('bodyOverflow').enableOverflow();
            }
        }
    }
</script>
<div x-data="initSizeGuidePanel()" x-defer="interact" class="flex flex-col gap-y-3">

(cm)<\/strong><\/td>\r\n<td>23cm<\/td>\r\n<td>24\/25cm<\/td>\r\n<td>25\/26cm<\/td>\r\n<td>27cm<\/td>\r\n<td>28cm<\/td>\r\n<td>29cm<\/td>\r\n<td>31cm<\/td>\r\n<\/tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>EU<\/strong><\/td>\r\n<td>35\/36<\/td>\r\n<td>37\/38<\/td>\r\n<td>39\/40<\/td>\r\n<td>41\/42<\/td>\r\n<td>43\/44<\/td>\r\n<td>45\/46<\/td>\r\n<td>47\/48<\/td>\r\n<\/tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>UK<\/strong><\/td>\r\n<td>3\/4<\/td>\r\n<td>4,5\/5<\/td>\r\n<td>6\/7<\/td>\r\n<td>7,5\/8<\/td>\r\n<td>9\/10<\/td>\r\n<td>11\/12<\/td>\r\n<td>13<\/td>\r\n<\/tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Taille recommand\u00e9e Havaianas<\/strong><\/td>\r\n<td>35\/36<\/td>\r\n<td>37\/38<\/td>\r\n<td>39\/40<\/td>\r\n<td>41\/42<\/td>\r\n<td>43\/44<\/td>\r\n<td>45\/46<\/td>\r\n<td>47\/48<\/td>\r\n<\/tr>\r\n<\/tbody>\r\n<\/table>\r\n<\/div>"},
            count: 0,
            activeTab: null,
            isTabEnable: false,
            sliderPosition: 0,
            sliderWidth: 0,
            init() {
                this.count = Object.keys(this.sizeGuides).length;
                this.isTabEnable = this.count > 1;
                this.activeTab = Object.keys(this.sizeGuides)[0];
                this.sliderWidth = `${100/this.count}%`;

            },
            changeActiveTab(activeTab) {
                if (!activeTab){ return }
                this.activeTab = activeTab;

                if (this.count === 0) { return }
                const index = Object.keys(this.sizeGuides).indexOf(activeTab) ?? 0;
                const leftPercentage = ( 100/this.count ) * index;
                this.sliderPosition = `${leftPercentage}%`;
            }
        }
    }
</script>
<div x-data="initSizeGuide()" x-defer="interact" class="size-guide-container">
    <template x-if="isTabEnable">
        <div>
            <div class="sticky top-0 flex bg-container text-lg text-center border-2 border-secondary-darker">
                <template x-for="(guide, index) in sizeGuides">
                    <span x-text="index" @click="changeActiveTab(index)"  class="block flex-1 py-4 cursor-pointer"></span>
                </template>
                <span class="block absolute top-0 h-full w-1/2 bg-primary mix-blend-difference pointer-events-none
                    transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out"
                    :style="{left: sliderPosition, width: sliderWidth}"
                ></span>
            </div>
            <template x-for="(guide, index) in sizeGuides">
                <div x-html="guide" x-show="activeTab === index"></div>
            </template>
        </div>
    </template>
    <template x-if="!isTabEnable">
        <template x-for="guide in sizeGuides">
            <div x-html="guide"></div>
        </template>
    </template>
</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
    </aside>
</div>




            </div>
        </div>
    </template>
</div>
<script>
    function initTab() {
        return {
            tabName: '',
            isTabVisible: false,
            isAccordionOpen: false,
            handleAccordionClick() {
                if (!this.isAccordionOpen) {
                    this.trackTabs(this.tabName);
                }

                this.isAccordionOpen = !this.isAccordionOpen;
            },
            trackTabs(tabName) {
                mhTracking.pushDataLayer({
                    event: 'shop',
                    product_click: `speedy fox patch comfort sweatshirt`,
                    action: 'click',
                    content_click: tabName
                })
            },
            eventListeners: {
                ['@event-selected-tab-changed.window'](event) {
                    this.isTabVisible = this.tabName === event.detail;
                }
            }
        }
    }
</script>
        </section>

            id="tab-material-care"
            class="[&:not(:first-of-type)]:border-t lg:border-none"

<script>
    function initSections() {
        return {
            activeTab: '',

            handleTabClick(tabName) {
                if (this.activeTab === tabName) {
                    return;
                }

                this.activeTab = tabName;
                this.dispatchTabChanged();

                this.trackTabs(tabName);
            },
            trackTabs(tabName) {
                mhTracking.pushDataLayer({
                    event: 'shop',
                    product_click: `speedy fox patch comfort sweatshirt`,
                    action: 'click',
                    content_click: tabName
                })
            },
            dispatchTabChanged() {
                window.dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('event-selected-tab-changed', {
                    detail: this.activeTab
                }));
            }
        }
    }
</script>
</div>
<script>
    const initRecommendSplideMobile = () => {
        return {
            dataAttribute: 'splideLazy',
            tileSelector: '[data-splide-lazy]',
            parents: document.getElementsByClassName('recommend-component'),
            lastTile: null,
            initSelector() {
                this.initMutationObserver();
            },
            initTilesBatch() {
                const tilesToInit = [...document.querySelectorAll(this.tileSelector)].slice(0, 4);
                tilesToInit.forEach((tile) => {
                    this.lastTile = tile;
                    tile.dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('scroll-mobile'));
                });
            },
            initMutationObserver() {
                const mutationObserver = new MutationObserver((mutationList) => {
                    for (let mutation of mutationList) {
                        if (mutation.type === 'childList' && mutation.target.className.includes('auc-Recommend')) {
                            this.initTilesBatch();
                            mutationObserver.disconnect();
                        }
                    }
                });

                Array.from(this.parents).forEach((elem) => mutationObserver.observe(elem, {childList: true, subtree: true}));
            },
            processScroll() {
                if (!this.lastTile) {
                    return;
                }

                if (window.scrollY >= this.lastTile.getBoundingClientRect().bottom) {
                    this.initTilesBatch();
                }
            }
        }
    }
</script>

        <div>
            <div class="algolia-product-selection-wrapper"
     x-bind:class="{'hidden': !isAllowed}"
     x-data="initProductSelection()"
     @private-content-loaded.window="getCartData($event.detail.data)"
>
    
    <!-- Algolia product selection scripts -->
    
<script>
    if (typeof productSelectionConfigProduct == "undefined") {
        function loadScript(url) {
            let script = document.createElement('script')
            script.setAttribute('type', 'text/javascript')
            script.setAttribute('src', url)
            document.head.append(script)

            return new Promise((resolve) => script.addEventListener('load', resolve))
        }

        function loadScripts(scripts) {
            window.algoliaLoading = true;
            return Promise.all(scripts.map(loadScript))
        }

        function getScriptsToLoad(productSelectionScripts) {
            const scripts = document.scripts;
            return productSelectionScripts.filter((algoliaScript) => {
                const scriptsContainingAlgolia = Array.from(scripts).filter((script) => {
                    if (!script.src) {
                        return false;
                    }

                    return script.src.includes(algoliaScript);
                })

                return !scriptsContainingAlgolia.length
            });
        }

        function loadScriptCallbackProduct(productSelectionConfigProduct ) {
            if (!window.algolia) {
                initAlgoliaCommon()
            }

            if (!window.algoliaAnalytics && typeof initInsights === 'function') {
                initInsights();
            }
            initAlgoliaProductSelectionForProduct(productSelectionConfigProduct );
        }

        function initProductSelectionProduct() {
            const productSelectionConfigProduct =
                {
                    "page": "product",
                    "suffix_index_name": "_products",
                    "container": "#related_products_look",
                    "nb_hits": "3",
                    "algolia_event_name": "look",
                    "filters": {"facets":{"objectID":["71216","76748"]}}                };
            const productSelectionScripts = ["https:\/\/static.maisonkitsune.com\/static\/version1749733577\/frontend\/MaisonHyva\/default\/en_US\/Hyva_AlgoliaSearch\/js\/internals\/instantsearch.production.min.js","https:\/\/static.maisonkitsune.com\/static\/version1749733577\/frontend\/MaisonHyva\/default\/en_US\/Hyva_AlgoliaSearch\/js\/common.js","https:\/\/static.maisonkitsune.com\/static\/version1749733577\/frontend\/MaisonHyva\/default\/en_US\/Hyva_AlgoliaSearch\/js\/internals\/search-insights.min.js","https:\/\/static.maisonkitsune.com\/static\/version1749733577\/frontend\/MaisonHyva\/default\/en_US\/Hyva_AlgoliaSearch\/js\/internals\/algoliasearch-lite.js"];
            const scriptsToLoad = getScriptsToLoad(productSelectionScripts);

            if (scriptsToLoad.length) {
                loadScripts(scriptsToLoad).then(() => {
                    window.algoliaLoading = false;
                    if (!window.algoliaLoadingInclude && !window.algoliaLoadingRecommend) {
                        if (window.algoliaScriptsToLoadInstant) {
                            window.algoliaScriptsToLoadInstant.forEach((script) => script());
                            window.algoliaScriptsToLoadInstant = [];
                        }

                        if (window.algoliaScriptsToLoadRecommend) {
                            window.algoliaScriptsToLoadRecommend.forEach((script) => script());
                            window.algoliaScriptsToLoadRecommend = [];
                        }

                        if (document.getElementById("instant-hit-template") !== null) {
                            if (window.algoliaScriptsToLoad) {
                                window.algoliaScriptsToLoad.forEach((script) => script());
                                window.algoliaScriptsToLoad = [];
                            }

                            loadScriptCallbackProduct(productSelectionConfigProduct);
                        } else {
                            window.algoliaScriptsToLoad = window.algoliaScriptsToLoad ? window.algoliaScriptsToLoad : [];
                            window.algoliaScriptsToLoad.push(loadScriptCallbackProduct.bind(this, productSelectionConfigProduct));
                        }
                    } else {
                        window.algoliaScriptsToLoad = window.algoliaScriptsToLoad ? window.algoliaScriptsToLoad : [];
                        window.algoliaScriptsToLoad.push(loadScriptCallbackProduct.bind(this, productSelectionConfigProduct));
                    }
                });
            } else {
                const isAlgogoLoading = window.algoliaLoading || window.algoliaLoadingInclude || window.algoliaLoadingRecommend;
                const isHitTemplateLoading = document.getElementById("instant-hit-template") === null;
                if (isAlgogoLoading || isHitTemplateLoading) {
                    window.algoliaScriptsToLoad = window.algoliaScriptsToLoad ? window.algoliaScriptsToLoad : [];
                    window.algoliaScriptsToLoad.push(loadScriptCallbackProduct.bind(this, productSelectionConfigProduct));
                } else {
                    loadScriptCallbackProduct(productSelectionConfigProduct);
                }
            }
        }

        function initAlgoliaProductSelectionForProduct(productSelectionConfigProduct ) {
            /** Redeclare filters which are already in productSelectionConfig, because Algolia seems to override these
            latters each time we use them in transformItems **/
            const filters = {"facets":{"objectID":["71216","76748"]}};

            const ctx = 'product';
            forceLoadSplide();
            selectors = {
                relatedTitle: '.product-related-tabs__content .title',
                algoliaResult: '.algolia-instant-selector-results',
                algoliaResultWrapper: '.algolia-instant-results-wrapper'
            };

            const searchClient = algoliasearch(algoliaConfig.applicationId, algoliaConfig.apiKey);
            const ruleContexts = ['magento_filters', ''];
            const originPage = productSelectionConfigProduct .page;

            ruleContexts.push('magento-landingpage-' + originPage);
            const format = window.isMobile() ? 'mobile' : 'desktop';

            let defaultFilters = productSelectionConfigProduct.filters.facets;

            const instantsearchOptions = {
                searchClient: searchClient,
                indexName: algoliaConfig.indexName + productSelectionConfigProduct.suffix_index_name,
                searchFunction: function (helper) {
                    if (productSelectionConfigProduct.filters) {
                        if (productSelectionConfigProduct.filters.numericRefinements) {
                            helper.state.numericRefinements = {
                                ...helper.state.numericRefinements,
                                ...productSelectionConfigProduct.filters.numericRefinements
                            }
                        }

                        if (defaultFilters) {
                            for (const [key, value] of Object.entries(defaultFilters)) {
                                if ((helper.state.disjunctiveFacetsRefinements[key] && !helper.state.disjunctiveFacetsRefinements[key].length) || typeof (helper.state.disjunctiveFacetsRefinements[key]) === "undefined") {
                                    helper.state.disjunctiveFacetsRefinements[key] = value;
                                }
                            }
                        }
                    }
                    helper.search();
                }
            }

            const searchParameters = {
                hitsPerPage: productSelectionConfigProduct.nb_hits,
                ruleContexts: ruleContexts,
                clickAnalytics: true,
                analyticsTags: [originPage, format],
                query: ''
            };

            const search = instantsearch(instantsearchOptions);

            search.addWidgets([
                instantsearch.widgets.hits(addHits()),
                instantsearch.widgets.configure(searchParameters),
            ]);

            const productSelectionMiddleWare = instantsearch.middlewares.createInsightsMiddleware({
                onEvent: (event) => {
                    const {insightsMethod, payload, widgetType, eventType} = event;
                    const query = search.helper.lastResults.query;

                    if (widgetType === 'ais.hits' && eventType === 'view') {
                        window.dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent(`product-selection-init-${ctx}`, {detail: {event}}));
                    }
                }
            });

            search.use(productSelectionMiddleWare);
            search.start();

            function addHits() {
                return {
                    container: productSelectionConfigProduct.container,
                    templates: {
                        empty: '',
                        item: document.getElementById("instant-hit-template").innerHTML
                    },
                    cssClasses: {
                        root: ["items__wrapper"],
                        list: ["products","list","items","product-items","grid","lg:grid-cols-4","grid-cols-2"],
                        item: ["item","product","product-item","h-fit"]                    },
                    transformItems: function (items) {
                                                    if(items && window.look_img_src) {
                                items.unshift({
                                    look_img_src: window.look_img_src
                                })
                            }
                        
                        if (filters && filters?.facets?.objectID) {
                            items.sort((a, b) => filters.facets.objectID.indexOf(a.objectID) - filters.facets.objectID.indexOf(b.objectID));
                        }

                        return items.map(function (item) {
                            item.__indexName = search.helper.lastResults.index;
                            item = transformHit(item, algoliaConfig.priceKey, search.helper);
                            item.eventName = productSelectionConfigProduct.algolia_event_name;
                            item.lazy_splide = true;
                            return item;
                        });
                    }
                };
            }
        }

        function forceLoadSplide() {
            if (!window.AlpineJSLoadedAlgolia && typeof Alpine !== 'undefined') {
                Alpine.store('hyva_splide_js').forceLoad();
                window.AlpineJSLoadedAlgolia = true;
            }
        }

        // Condition for the Algolia minicart crossell, because this template is generic
                    initProductSelectionProduct();
            }
</script>

            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row">
            <div id="related_products_look" class="px-px"></div>
        </div>
    </div>

            isAllowed: !!1,
            getCartData(data) {
                this.isAllowed = !data.cart?.preorder;
            }
        }
    }
</script>

     style="--delay: 0ms"
     x-data="initCountdown_684bc01b70ac1()"
     :class="{'translate-y-full lg:opacity-0 pointer-events-none': !intervalTimer, 'translate-y-0 full lg:opacity-100 delay-[var(--delay)] pointer-events-auto': intervalTimer}">
    <div class="bg-primary grid lg:grid-cols-[auto_auto] lg:w-fit lg:w-[974px] mx-auto py-4 px-10 lg:px-4 items-center shadow-[0_0_20px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.25)] gap-4 relative lg:static">

                    <p class="text-xl lg:text-2xl font-bold" x-text="remainingDays">XX</p>
                    <p class="text-sm text-primary-lighter">days</p>
                </div>

                <div class="text-center">
                    <p class="text-xl lg:text-2xl font-bold" x-text="remainingHours">XX</p>
                    <p class="text-sm text-primary-lighter">hours</p>
                </div>

                <div class="text-center">
                    <p class="text-xl lg:text-2xl font-bold" x-text="remainingMinutes">XX</p>
                    <p class="text-sm text-primary-lighter">minutes</p>
                </div>

                <div class="text-center">
                    <p class="text-xl lg:text-2xl font-bold" x-text="remainingSeconds">XX</p>

                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="w-10 h-10 cursor-pointer absolute top-0 right-0 lg:static" alt="Close" @click="closeCountdown()" role="img">
<path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M12 12.7071L17.3033 18.0104L18.0104 17.3033L12.7071 12L18.0104 6.6967L17.3033 5.98959L12 11.2929L6.69669 5.98959L5.98959 6.69669L11.2929 12L5.98958 17.3033L6.69669 18.0104L12 12.7071Z" fill="#202020"/>
<title>x</title></svg>

<script>
    'use strict';

    function initCountdown_684bc01b70ac1() {
        return {
            cookieName: 'countdown-6538',
            cookieLifetime: 2,
            intervalTimer: null,
            dateCountdown: new Date('2025\u002D06\u002D24T21\u003A59\u003A00\u002B00\u003A00'),
            dateNow: new Date(new Date().toUTCString().substring(0, 25)), // New date object with UTC timezone
            dateDifference: 0,
            remainingDays: 0,
            remainingDaysInt: 0,
            remainingHours: 0,
            remainingHoursInt: 0,
            remainingMinutes: 0,
            remainingMinutesInt: 0,
            remainingSeconds: 0,
            remainingSecondsInt: 0,

            init() {
                if (hyva.getCookie(this.cookieName)) {
                    return;
                }

                if (this.dateNow > this.dateCountdown) {
                    return;
                }

                this.dateDifference = Math.abs(this.dateCountdown - this.dateNow);
                this.refreshCountdown();
                this.intervalTimer = setInterval(this.refreshCountdown.bind(this), 1000);
            },
            refreshCountdown() {
                let delta = this.dateDifference / 1000;

                this.remainingDaysInt = Math.floor(delta / 86400);
                delta -= this.remainingDaysInt * 86400;
                this.remainingDays = this.zeroPadUnit(this.remainingDaysInt);

                this.remainingHoursInt = Math.floor(delta / 3600) % 24;
                delta -= this.remainingHoursInt * 3600;
                this.remainingHours = this.zeroPadUnit(this.remainingHoursInt);

                this.remainingMinutesInt = Math.floor(delta / 60) % 60;
                delta -= this.remainingMinutesInt * 60;
                this.remainingMinutes = this.zeroPadUnit(this.remainingMinutesInt);

                this.remainingSecondsInt = Math.floor(delta % 60);
                this.remainingSeconds = this.zeroPadUnit(this.remainingSecondsInt);

                this.dateDifference -= 1000;

                this.checkInterval();
            },
            zeroPadUnit(value) {
                return `${value}`.length < 2 ? `0${value}` : value;
            },
            checkInterval() {
                if (this.dateDifference >= 1000) {
                    return;
                }
                this.clearIntervalTimer();
            },
            closeCountdown() {
                this.clearIntervalTimer();

                if (!this.cookieLifetime) {
                    return;
                }
                hyva.setCookie(this.cookieName, true, this.cookieLifetime);
            },
            clearIntervalTimer() {
                this.dateDifference = null;
                clearInterval(this.intervalTimer);
                this.intervalTimer = null;
            }
        }
    }
</script>
</main><footer class="page-footer"><div class="footer content">

    'usp_footer_b_country_code',
    maisonHyva.getCountryCookieCode()

     x-defer="intersect"

    <template x-if="result !== ''">
        <div class="px-4 py-8 md:p-8 border-t border-gray-light">
            <div class="md:container"

<script>
    const switcherWrapper = document.getElementsByClassName('switcher-wrapper')[0];
    const storeFlagWrapper = document.getElementsByClassName('store-switcher-wrapper')[0];

    if(storeFlagWrapper) {
        const callback = function(mutationsList) {
            for (const mutation of mutationsList) {
                if (mutation.type === 'childList' && switcherWrapper) {
                    switcherWrapper.classList.remove('opacity-0');
                    switcherWrapper.classList.add('opacity-100');
                    observer.disconnect();
                }
            }
        }
        const observer = new MutationObserver(callback);
        observer.observe(storeFlagWrapper, {attributes: false, childList: true, subtree: true});
    }

</script>

<script>
    (() => {
        function src_default(Alpine) {
            Alpine.directive("intersect", (el, { value, expression, modifiers }, { evaluateLater, cleanup }) => {
                let evaluate = evaluateLater(expression);
                let options = {
                    rootMargin: getRootMargin(modifiers),
                    threshold: getThreshhold(modifiers)
                };
                let observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
                    entries.forEach((entry) => {
                        if (entry.isIntersecting === (value === "leave"))
                            return;
                        evaluate();
                        modifiers.includes("once") && observer.disconnect();
                    });
                }, options);
                observer.observe(el);
                cleanup(() => {
                    observer.disconnect();
                });
            });
        }
        function getThreshhold(modifiers) {
            if (modifiers.includes("full"))
                return 0.99;
            if (modifiers.includes("half"))
                return 0.5;
            if (!modifiers.includes("threshold"))
                return 0;
            let threshold = modifiers[modifiers.indexOf("threshold") + 1];
            if (threshold === "100")
                return 1;
            if (threshold === "0")
                return 0;
            return Number(`.${threshold}`);
        }
        function getLengthValue(rawValue) {
            let match = rawValue.match(/^(-?[0-9]+)(px|%)?$/);
            return match ? match[1] + (match[2] || "px") : void 0;
        }
        function getRootMargin(modifiers) {
            const key = "margin";
            const fallback = "0px 0px 0px 0px";
            const index = modifiers.indexOf(key);
            if (index === -1)
                return fallback;
            let values = [];
            for (let i = 1; i < 5; i++) {
                values.push(getLengthValue(modifiers[index + i] || ""));
            }
            values = values.filter((v) => v !== void 0);
            return values.length ? values.join(" ").trim() : fallback;
        }

        document.addEventListener("alpine:init", () => {
            window.Alpine.plugin(src_default);
        });
    })();
</script>
<script>
    for (const [selector, deferUntil] of Object.entries({".product-slider section[x-data]":"intersect",".product-info [x-data]":"intersect","#filters-content [x-data]":"intersect","#review_form":"intersect","section[x-data^=initRecentlyViewedProductsComponent]":"intersect","div[x-data^=initBundleOptions]":"intersect","#product_addtocart_form [x-data]":"intersect","#notice-cookie-block":"intersect"})) {
        document.querySelectorAll(selector).forEach(el => el.setAttribute('x-defer', `${deferUntil}`));
    }
</script>
<script>
    (function () {
        "use strict";

        const hasAlpine = new Promise(resolve => {
            window.addEventListener('alpine:initialized', resolve, {once: true, passive: true});
        });

        const hasInteract = new Promise(resolve => {
            (events => {
                const onInteract = () => {
                    resolve();
                    events.forEach(type => window.removeEventListener(type, onInteract));
                }
                events.forEach(type => window.addEventListener(type, onInteract, {once: true, passive: true}))
            })(['touchstart', 'mouseover', 'wheel', 'scroll', 'keydown'])
        });

        const onIntersect = (el) => {
            return new Promise(resolve => {
                const observer = new IntersectionObserver(entries => {
                    for (const entry of entries) {
                        if (entry.isIntersecting) {
                            observer.disconnect()
                            resolve();
                        }
                    }
                }, {});
                observer.observe(el);
            });
        }

        function runComponent(el) {
            hasAlpine.then(() => {
                el.removeAttribute('x-ignore');
                queueMicrotask(() => Alpine.initTree(el));
            });
        }

        function initDeferredComponents() {
            document.querySelectorAll('[x-data][x-defer]').forEach(el => {
                el.setAttribute('x-ignore', '');
                const deferUntil = (el.getAttribute('x-defer') || '').trim();
                switch (deferUntil) {
                    case 'interact':
                        hasInteract.then(() => runComponent(el));
                        break;
                    case 'intersect':
                        onIntersect(el).then(() => runComponent(el))
                        break;
                    case 'idle':
                        window.requestIdleCallback
                            ? window.requestIdleCallback(() => runComponent(el), {timeout: 4000})
                            : setTimeout(() => runComponent(el), 4000);
                        break;
                    case 'eager':
                        runComponent(el);
                        break;
                    default:
                        if (deferUntil.startsWith('event:') && deferUntil.length > 6) {
                            window.addEventListener(deferUntil.substring(6), () => runComponent(el), {once: true, passive: true});
                        }
                }
            });
        }

        window.addEventListener('alpine:init', initDeferredComponents, {once: true, passive: true});
    })()
</script>
<script>
    (() => {
        function loadJSLightboxLibrary() {
            return import('https://static.maisonkitsune.com/static/version1749733577/frontend/MaisonHyva/default/en_US/Blackbird_HyvaPhotoSwipe/js/photoswipe-lightbox.esm.min.js');
        }
        function loadJSLibrary() {
            return import('https://static.maisonkitsune.com/static/version1749733577/frontend/MaisonHyva/default/en_US/Blackbird_HyvaPhotoSwipe/js/photoswipe.esm.min.js');
        }
        function loadCssLibrary() {
            return new Promise(resolve => {
                const link = document.createElement('link');
                link.rel = "stylesheet";
                link.type = "text/css";
                link.href = 'https://static.maisonkitsune.com/static/version1749733577/frontend/MaisonHyva/default/en_US/Blackbird_HyvaPhotoSwipe/css/photoswipe.min.css';
                link.onload = resolve;
                document.head.appendChild(link);
            })
        }

        function loadScripts() {
            if(isScriptAdded()){
                return;
            }

            Promise.all([loadJSLightboxLibrary(), loadJSLibrary(), loadCssLibrary()])
                .then((results) => setWindowVariable(results));
        }
        function setWindowVariable(results) {
            const requiredClasses = ["PhotoSwipe","PhotoSwipeLightbox"];
            const resultsWithClasses = results.filter((current) => current.default);
            const classes = resultsWithClasses
                .reduce((result, current) => {
                    result[current.default.name] = current.default;
                    return result;
                }, {});

            let successImportedClasses = 0;

            requiredClasses.forEach((requiredClass) => {
                if (!Object.keys(classes).includes(requiredClass)) {
                    throw new Error(`[HyvaPhotoSwipe] Could not load the required class ${requiredClass}`);
                }

                window[requiredClass] = classes[requiredClass];
                successImportedClasses++;
            });

            if (successImportedClasses === requiredClasses.length) {
                Alpine.store('hyva_photo_swipe').is_loaded = true;
            }
        }
        function isScriptAdded() {
            const requiredClasses = ["PhotoSwipe","PhotoSwipeLightbox"];

            let successImportedClasses = 0;

            requiredClasses.forEach((requiredClass) => {
                if (!window[requiredClass]) {
                    return;
                }

                successImportedClasses++;
            });

            return successImportedClasses === requiredClasses.length;
        }
        function isPhotoSwipeRequired() {
            const scriptElements = document.querySelectorAll('script');

            return Array.from(scriptElements).filter((script) => {
                const scriptContent = script.textContent || script.innerText;

                // Specific string searched, compatible with JS minified, ignore this script
                return scriptContent.includes('PhotoSwipeLightbox(') && !scriptContent.includes('isPhotoSwipeRequired');
            }).length;
        }

        function initializeStoreState() {
            Alpine.store('hyva_photo_swipe', {
                is_loaded: false,

                forceLoad() {
                    loadScripts();
                }
            });
        }

        document.addEventListener("alpine:init", () => {
            initializeStoreState();

            if (!isPhotoSwipeRequired()) {
                return;
            }

            loadScripts();
        });
    })();
</script>
<script>
    (() => {
        function loadJSLibrary() {
            return new Promise(resolve => {
                const script = document.createElement('script');
                script.type = 'text/javascript';
                script.src = 'https://static.maisonkitsune.com/static/version1749733577/frontend/MaisonHyva/default/en_US/Blackbird_HyvaSplideJs/js/splide.min.js';
                script.async = true;
                script.onload = resolve;
                document.head.appendChild(script);
            })
        }
        function loadCssLibrary() {
            return new Promise(resolve => {
                const link = document.createElement('link');
                link.rel = "stylesheet";
                link.type = "text/css";
                link.href = 'https://static.maisonkitsune.com/static/version1749733577/frontend/MaisonHyva/default/en_US/Blackbird_HyvaSplideJs/css/splide.min.css';
                link.onload = resolve;
                document.head.appendChild(link);
            })
        }

        function loadScripts() {
            if(isScriptAdded()){
                return;
            }

            Promise.all([loadJSLibrary(), loadCssLibrary()]).then(() => updateStoreState());
        }
        function updateStoreState() {
            Alpine.store('hyva_splide_js').is_loaded = true;
        }
        function isScriptAdded() {
            const scripts = document.scripts;
            const scriptsContainingSplide = Array.from(scripts).filter((script) => {
                if(!script.src){
                    return false;
                }

                return script.src.includes(
                    'splide.min.js'
                );
            })

            return scriptsContainingSplide.length;
        }

        function initializeStoreState() {
            Alpine.store('hyva_splide_js', {
                is_loaded: false,

                forceLoad() {
                    loadScripts();
                }
            });
        }

        document.addEventListener("alpine:init", () => {
            initializeStoreState();

            if (!document.getElementsByClassName('splide').length) {
                return;
            }

            loadScripts();
        });
    })();
</script>

<script type="module"
        src="https://static.maisonkitsune.com/static/version1749733577/frontend/MaisonHyva/default/en_US/Hyva_Theme/js/alpine3.min.js"
        defer
        crossorigin
></script>
<script>
    'use strict';
    function dispatchMessages(messages, hideAfter) {
        const messagesEvent = new CustomEvent("messages-loaded", {
            detail: {
                messages: messages,
                hideAfter: hideAfter
            }
        });
        window.dispatchEvent(messagesEvent);
    }

    if (typeof hyva === 'undefined' || (!hyva.getBrowserStorage || !hyva.getCookie || !hyva.setCookie)) {
        console.warn("Hyvä helpers are not loaded yet. Make sure they are included before this script");
    }

    (function( hyva, undefined ) {

        hyva.initFormKey = () => {
            const inputSelector = 'input[name="form_key"]',
                formKey = hyva.getFormKey();

            Array.from(document.querySelectorAll(inputSelector)).map(function (input) {
                input.value = formKey
            });
        }

        hyva.initMessages = () => {
            try {
                const messages = hyva.getCookie('mage-messages');
                window.mageMessages = messages ? JSON.parse(decodeURIComponent(messages).replace(/\+/g, ' ')) : [];

                dispatchMessages(window.mageMessages);

                                // empty `mage-messages` cookie
                const skipSetDomain = true;
                hyva.setCookie('mage-messages','', -1, skipSetDomain);

            } catch (error) {
                console.warn('Error parsing Cookie Messages:', error);
            }
        }

        window.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', hyva.initFormKey);
        hyva.alpineInitialized(hyva.initMessages)

    }( window.hyva = window.hyva || {} ));
</script>
<script>
    'use strict';
    {
        const private_content_key = 'mage-cache-storage';
        const private_content_expire_key = 'mage-cache-timeout';
        const private_content_version_key = 'private_content_version';
        const section_data_ids_key = 'section_data_ids';
        const mage_cache_session_id_key = 'mage-cache-sessid';
        const last_visited_store_key = 'last_visited_store';

        const ttl = 3600;

        if (typeof hyva === 'undefined' || (!hyva.getBrowserStorage || !hyva.getCookie || !hyva.setCookie)) {
            console.warn("Hyvä helpers are not loaded yet. Make sure they are included before this script");
        }

        function loadSectionData () {
            const browserStorage = hyva.getBrowserStorage();
            if (!browserStorage) {
                typeof window.dispatchMessages !== "undefined" && window.dispatchMessages(
                    [{
                        type: "warning",
                        text: "Please enable LocalStorage in your browser."
                    }]
                );
                return;
            }
            try {
                let isInvalid = false;

                if (hyva.getCookie(last_visited_store_key) !== CURRENT_STORE_CODE) {
                    isInvalid = true;
                }
                hyva.setCookie(last_visited_store_key, CURRENT_STORE_CODE, false, false);

                if (!hyva.getCookie(mage_cache_session_id_key)) {
                    isInvalid = true;
                    browserStorage.removeItem(private_content_key);
                    const skipSetDomain = true;
                    const days = false;
                    hyva.setCookie(mage_cache_session_id_key, true, days, skipSetDomain)
                }

                const cookieVersion = hyva.getCookie(private_content_version_key);
                const storageVersion = browserStorage.getItem(private_content_version_key);

                if (cookieVersion && !storageVersion || cookieVersion !== storageVersion) {
                    isInvalid = true;
                }

                const privateContentExpires = browserStorage.getItem(private_content_expire_key);
                if (privateContentExpires && new Date(privateContentExpires) < new Date()) {
                    browserStorage.removeItem(private_content_key);
                }

                if (isInvalid && cookieVersion) {
                    fetchPrivateContent([]);
                } else if (cookieVersion && storageVersion && cookieVersion === storageVersion) {
                    const privateContent = JSON.parse(browserStorage.getItem(private_content_key));
                    if (
                        privateContent &&
                        privateContentExpires &&
                        privateContent.cart &&
                        privateContent.customer
                    ) {
                        dispatchPrivateContent(privateContent);
                    } else {
                        fetchPrivateContent([]);
                    }
                } else {
                    if (document.getElementById('default-section-data')) {
                        const privateContent = JSON.parse(document.getElementById('default-section-data').innerText.trim());
                        dispatchPrivateContent(privateContent);
                    } else {
                        dispatchPrivateContent({});
                    }
                }

            } catch (error) {
                console.warn('Error retrieving Private Content:', error);
            }
        }

        hyva.alpineInitialized(loadSectionData)
        window.addEventListener('reload-customer-section-data', loadSectionData);

        function dispatchPrivateContent(data) {
            const privateContentEvent = new CustomEvent("private-content-loaded", {
                detail: {
                    data: data
                }
            });
            window.dispatchEvent(privateContentEvent);
        }

        function fetchPrivateContent(sections) {
            fetch(`${BASE_URL}customer/section/load/?sections=${encodeURIComponent(sections.join(','))}`, {
                method: 'GET',
                headers: {
                    'Content-Type': 'application/json',
                    'X-Requested-With': 'XMLHttpRequest'
                }
            })
                .then(response => response.json())
                .then(
                    data => {
                        if (data) {
                            try {
                                const browserStorage = hyva.getBrowserStorage();

                                // merge new data preserving non-invalidated sections
                                const oldSectionData = JSON.parse(browserStorage.getItem(private_content_key) || '{}') || {};

                                if ((! data.cart || ! data.cart.cartId) && oldSectionData['checkout-data']) {
                                    delete oldSectionData['checkout-data'];
                                }
                                const newSectionData = Object.assign(oldSectionData, data);

                                dispatchPrivateContent(newSectionData);

                                // don't persist messages, they've been dispatched already
                                if (newSectionData.messages && newSectionData.messages.messages ) {
                                    newSectionData.messages.messages = [];
                                }

                                browserStorage.setItem(private_content_key, JSON.stringify(newSectionData));

                                const expiresAt = new Date(Date.now() + (ttl * 1000)).toISOString();
                                browserStorage.setItem(private_content_expire_key, expiresAt);

                                const newCookieVersion = hyva.getCookie(private_content_version_key);
                                browserStorage.setItem(private_content_version_key, newCookieVersion);

                                // We don't need the section_data_ids in Hyvä, but we store them for compatibility
                                // with Luma Fallback. Otherwise, not all sections are loaded in Luma Checkout
                                hyva.setCookie(
                                    section_data_ids_key,
                                    JSON.stringify(
                                        Object.keys(data).reduce((sectionDataIds, sectionKey) => {
                                            sectionDataIds[sectionKey] = data[sectionKey]['data_id'];
                                            return sectionDataIds;
                                        }, {})
                                    ),
                                    false,
                                    true
                                );
                            } catch (error) {
                                console.warn("Couldn't store privateContent", error);
                            }
                        }
                    }
                );
        }
    }
</script>

    })()
</script>
