<script type="text/template" id="current-refinements-template">
    <div class="cross-wrapper">
        <span class="clear-cross clear-refinement"></span>
    </div>
    <div class="current-refinement-wrapper">
        {{#label}}
        <span class="current-refinement-label">{{label}}{{^operator}}:{{/operator}}</span>
        {{/label}}
        {{#operator}}
        {{{displayOperator}}}
        {{/operator}}
        {{#exclude}}-{{/exclude}}
        <span class="current-refinement-name">{{name}}</span>
    </div>
</script><script>
    'use strict';

    function initParentContainerProcessor() {
        const selectors = {
            labelContainer: '.amasty-label-container',
            galleryImg: '#gallery img:not(.amasty-label-image)'
        }

        return {
            /**
             * @param {AmlabelComponent} label
             * @return {void}
             */
            process: function (label) {
                this.moveLabelToParent(label);
            },

            /**
             * @param {AmlabelComponent} label
             * @return {void}
             */
            moveLabelToParent: function (label) {
                const newParent = this.getNewParent(label);

                if (!newParent) {
                    return;
                }

                const wrapperElement = newParent.querySelector(label.wrapperClass);
                label.parent = newParent;

                // if same wrapper already exists - move label there
                if (wrapperElement && !wrapperElement.isSameNode(label.element)) {
                    this.insertLabelByPriority(label, wrapperElement);
                } else {
                    newParent.prepend(label.element);
                }
            },

            /**
             * @param {AmlabelComponent} label
             * @return {HTMLElement|null}
             */
            getNewParent: function (label) {
                return document.querySelector(selectors.gallery)?.parentElement;
            },

            /**
             * @param {AmlabelComponent} label
             * @param {HTMLElement} wrapperElement
             * @return {void}
             */
            insertLabelByPriority: function (label, wrapperElement) {
                const labelContainers = wrapperElement.querySelectorAll(selectors.labelContainer);
                const currentLabelOrder = label.labelContainer.dataset.amlabelOrder;
                let insertAfterContainer = null;

                // find the label behind which we want to insert current one by priority
                labelContainers.forEach(labelContainer => {
                    if (labelContainer.dataset.amlabelOrder < currentLabelOrder) {
                        insertAfterContainer = labelContainer;
                    }
                });

                insertAfterContainer === null
                    ? wrapperElement.prepend(label.labelContainer)
                    : insertAfterContainer.after(label.labelContainer);

                label.element.remove();
                label.element = wrapperElement;
            }
        }
    }
</script>
<script>
    'use strict';

    function initLabelItemProcessor() {
        /**
         * @typedef {Object} AmlabelComponent
         *
         * @property {HTMLElement} element Label wrapper element
         * @property {HTMLElement} parent Element where label should be placed
         * @property {boolean} initialized Is label initialized
         * @property {string} wrapperClass Dynamic class for label wrapper to place multiple labels properly by position
         * @property {HTMLElement} labelContainer Container for label text image and tooltip
         * @property {Config} config Label Configuration
         * @property {Object} parentContainerProcessor
         * @property {Object} labelItemProcessor
         */

        /**
         * @typedef {Object} AmLabelConfig
         *
         * @property {0|1} alignment Labels Alignment config value (0 - Horizontal| 1 - Vertical)
         * @property {number} label Label Id
         * @property {number} margin Margin between labels config value
         * @property {('cat'|'prod')} mode Label mode
         * @property {number} move
         * @property {number} order Label order
         * @property {string} path The css selector to which label should place
         * @property {string} position Label position
         * @property {string} product Product Id
         * @property {string} redirect_url
         * @property {string} size Label size
         * @property {{
         *     backgroundColor: string,
         *     color: string,
         *     content: string,
         *     status: 1|2|3
         * }} tooltip
         */

        return {
            /**
             * @param {AmlabelComponent} label
             * @return {void}
             */
            process: function(label) {
                this.setLabelSize(label);
                this.setLinkProps(label);
            },

            /**
             * @param {AmlabelComponent} label
             * @return {void}
             */
            setLabelSize: function (label) {
                if (!label.config.size) {
                    return;
                }

                label.labelContainer.style.width = label.parent.offsetWidth * label.config.size / 100 + 'px';
            },

            /**
             *
             * @param {Object} $event
             * @param {HTMLElement} tooltipNode
             */
            placeTooltip: function($event, tooltipNode) {
                const labelNode = $event.target;
                const labelNodeRect = labelNode.getBoundingClientRect();

                tooltipNode.style.bottom = (window.innerHeight - labelNodeRect.top)  + 'px';
                tooltipNode.style.left = (labelNodeRect.left + labelNode.offsetWidth / 2 ) + 'px';
            },

            /**
             * @param {AmlabelComponent} label
             * @return {void}
             */
            setLinkProps: function (label) {
                !!label.config.redirect_url && label.labelContainer.classList.add('-link', 'cursor-pointer');
            },

            /**
             * @param {Object} $event Click event
             * @param {string} redirectUrl
             */
            openLink: function($event, redirectUrl) {
                if (redirectUrl.length === 0) {
                    return;
                }

                $event.preventDefault();
                window.open(redirectUrl, '_blank');
            }
        }
    }
</script>
    <script>
        const instantsearchScripts = ["https:\/\/static.maisonkitsune.com\/static\/version1749733577\/frontend\/MaisonHyva\/default\/en_US\/Hyva_AlgoliaSearch\/js\/internals\/instantsearch.production.min.js","https:\/\/static.maisonkitsune.com\/static\/version1749733577\/frontend\/MaisonHyva\/default\/en_US\/Hyva_AlgoliaSearch\/js\/common.js","https:\/\/static.maisonkitsune.com\/static\/version1749733577\/frontend\/MaisonHyva\/default\/en_US\/Hyva_AlgoliaSearch\/js\/internals\/search-insights.min.js","https:\/\/static.maisonkitsune.com\/static\/version1749733577\/frontend\/MaisonHyva\/default\/en_US\/Hyva_AlgoliaSearch\/js\/internals\/algoliasearch-lite.js","https:\/\/static.maisonkitsune.com\/static\/version1749733577\/frontend\/MaisonHyva\/default\/en_US\/Hyva_AlgoliaSearch\/js\/internals\/hogan.min.js","https:\/\/static.maisonkitsune.com\/static\/version1749733577\/frontend\/MaisonHyva\/default\/en_US\/Hyva_AlgoliaSearch\/js\/instantsearch.js"]
        const recommendedScripts = ["https:\/\/static.maisonkitsune.com\/static\/version1749733577\/frontend\/MaisonHyva\/default\/en_US\/Hyva_AlgoliaSearch\/js\/internals\/instantsearch.production.min.js","https:\/\/static.maisonkitsune.com\/static\/version1749733577\/frontend\/MaisonHyva\/default\/en_US\/Hyva_AlgoliaSearch\/js\/common.js","https:\/\/static.maisonkitsune.com\/static\/version1749733577\/frontend\/MaisonHyva\/default\/en_US\/Hyva_AlgoliaSearch\/js\/internals\/search-insights.min.js","https:\/\/static.maisonkitsune.com\/static\/version1749733577\/frontend\/MaisonHyva\/default\/en_US\/Hyva_AlgoliaSearch\/js\/internals\/recommend.min.js","https:\/\/static.maisonkitsune.com\/static\/version1749733577\/frontend\/MaisonHyva\/default\/en_US\/Hyva_AlgoliaSearch\/js\/internals\/recommend-js.min.js","https:\/\/static.maisonkitsune.com\/static\/version1749733577\/frontend\/MaisonHyva\/default\/en_US\/Hyva_AlgoliaSearch\/js\/recommend.js"]
        const instantSearchConfigHeader = {context: 'header'};

        function loadScript(url) {
            let script = document.createElement('script');
            script.setAttribute('type', 'text/javascript');
            script.setAttribute('src', url);
            document.head.append(script);

            return new Promise((resolve) => script.addEventListener('load', resolve));
        }

        function loadScripts(scripts, loading) {
            window[loading] = true;
            return Promise.all(scripts.map(loadScript));
        }

        function getScriptsToLoad(algoliaScripts) {
            const scripts = document.scripts;
            return algoliaScripts.filter((algoliaScript) => {
                const scriptsContainingAlgolia = Array.from(scripts).filter((script) => {
                    if (!script.src) {
                        return false;
                    }

                    return script.src.includes(algoliaScript);
                })

                return !scriptsContainingAlgolia.length
            });
        }

        function initInstantSearch(config) {
            const scriptsToLoad = getScriptsToLoad(instantsearchScripts);
            const callbackLoadScript = () => {
                if (!window.algolia) {
                    initAlgoliaCommon();
                }
                if (!window.algoliaAnalytics && typeof initInsights === 'function') {
                    initInsights();
                }

                initAlgoliaInstantSearch(config);
            };

            if (scriptsToLoad.length) {
                loadScripts(scriptsToLoad, 'algoliaLoadingInclude').then(() => {
                    window.algoliaLoadingInclude = false;
                    if (!window.algoliaLoadingRecommend && !window.algoliaLoading) {
                        if (window.algoliaScriptsToLoadInstant) {
                            window.algoliaScriptsToLoadInstant.forEach((script) => script());
                            window.algoliaScriptsToLoadInstant = [];
                        }
                        if (window.algoliaScriptsToLoad) {
                            window.algoliaScriptsToLoad.forEach((script) => script());
                            window.algoliaScriptsToLoad = [];
                        }
                        if (window.algoliaScriptsToLoadRecommend) {
                            window.algoliaScriptsToLoadRecommend.forEach((script) => script());
                            window.algoliaScriptsToLoadRecommend = [];
                        }
                        callbackLoadScript();
                    } else {
                        window.algoliaScriptsToLoadRecommend = window.algoliaScriptsToLoadRecommend ? window.algoliaScriptsToLoadRecommend : [];
                        window.algoliaScriptsToLoadRecommend.push(callbackLoadScript);
                    }
                });
            } else {
                if (window.algoliaLoading || window.algoliaLoadingInclude || window.algoliaLoadingRecommend) {
                    window.algoliaScriptsToLoadInstant = window.algoliaScriptsToLoadInstant ? window.algoliaScriptsToLoadInstant : [];
                    window.algoliaScriptsToLoadInstant.push(callbackLoadScript);
                } else {
                    callbackLoadScript();
                }
            }
        }

        function initRecommended() {
            const scriptsToLoad = getScriptsToLoad(recommendedScripts);
            const callbackLoadScript = () => {
                if (!window.algolia) {
                    initAlgoliaCommon();
                }
                if (!window.algoliaAnalytics && typeof initInsights === 'function') {
                    initInsights();
                }
                initAlgoliaRecommended('catalog_product_view', ["75900"]);
            }

            if (scriptsToLoad.length) {
                loadScripts(scriptsToLoad, 'algoliaLoadingRecommend').then(() => {
                    window.algoliaLoadingRecommend = false;
                    if (!window.algoliaLoadingInclude && !window.algoliaLoading) {
                        if (window.algoliaScriptsToLoadInstant) {
                            window.algoliaScriptsToLoadInstant.forEach((script) => script());
                            window.algoliaScriptsToLoadInstant = [];
                        }
                        if (window.algoliaScriptsToLoad) {
                            window.algoliaScriptsToLoad.forEach((script) => script());
                            window.algoliaScriptsToLoad = [];
                        }
                        if (window.algoliaScriptsToLoadRecommend) {
                            window.algoliaScriptsToLoadRecommend.forEach((script) => script());
                            window.algoliaScriptsToLoadRecommend = [];
                        }
                        callbackLoadScript();
                    } else {
                        window.algoliaScriptsToLoadRecommend = window.algoliaScriptsToLoadRecommend ? window.algoliaScriptsToLoadRecommend : [];
                        window.algoliaScriptsToLoadRecommend.push(callbackLoadScript);
                    }
                });
            } else {
                if (window.algoliaLoading || window.algoliaLoadingInclude || window.algoliaLoadingRecommend) {
                    window.algoliaScriptsToLoadRecommend = window.algoliaScriptsToLoadRecommend ? window.algoliaScriptsToLoadRecommend : [];
                    window.algoliaScriptsToLoadRecommend.push(callbackLoadScript);
                } else {
                    callbackLoadScript();
                }
            }
        }

        //init for header
        if (!algoliaConfig.isSearchPage) {
            initInstantSearch(instantSearchConfigHeader);
        }

        if (algoliaConfig.instant.enabled && (algoliaConfig.isCategoryPage || algoliaConfig.isSearchPage)) {
            initInstantSearch({});
        }

                if (algoliaConfig.recommend.enabledFBT || algoliaConfig.recommend.enabledRelated) {
            initRecommended()
        }
        
        window.addEventListener('OneTrustGroupsUpdated', function () {
            initInsights(true);
        });
    </script>

<script>
    function initInsights(partial = false) {
        window.algoliaAnalytics = AlgoliaAnalytics.default;
        window.hasAddedParameters = false;

        function getAlgoliaConsent() {
            
            return JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem('ALGOLIA_CONSENT'));
        }

        if (algoliaConfig) {
            addSearchParameters();

            try {
                window.algoliaConsent = getAlgoliaConsent();

                if (!window.algoliaConsent) {
                    maisonHyva.verifyGroupAgainstOneTrust(algoliaConfig.personalization?.onetrust_group_id);
                }

                if (window.algoliaConsent) {
                    initializeAnalytics(partial);
                }
            } catch (error) {
                console.log(`An error happened when trying to initialize analytics : ${error.message}`);
            }
        }

        // Although events can accept both auth and anon tokens, queries can only accept a single token
        function determineUserToken() {
            return window.algoliaAnalytics.getUserToken();
        }


        function initializeAnalytics(partial = false) {
            if (partial) {
                algoliaAnalytics.init({
                    appId: algoliaConfig.applicationId,
                    apiKey: algoliaConfig.apiKey,
                    partial: true,
                    useCookie: true
                });
            } else {
                algoliaAnalytics.init({
                    appId: algoliaConfig.applicationId,
                    apiKey: algoliaConfig.apiKey,
                    useCookie: true,
                });
            }

            let userAgent = 'insights-js-in-magento (' + algoliaConfig.extensionVersion + ')';
            window.algoliaAnalytics.addAlgoliaAgent(userAgent);

            let unsetAuthenticationToken = hyva.getCookie('unset_authentication_token');

            if (hyva.getCookie('aa-search') && hyva.getCookie('aa-search') !== '') {
                window.algoliaAnalytics.setUserToken(hyva.getCookie('aa-search'));
            } else if (hyva.getCookie('_ALGOLIA') && hyva.getCookie('_ALGOLIA') !== '') {
                window.algoliaAnalytics.setUserToken(hyva.getCookie('_ALGOLIA'));
            } else if (unsetAuthenticationToken && unsetAuthenticationToken !== '') {
                window.algoliaAnalytics.setUserToken('undefined');
                hyva.setCookie('unset_authentication_token', '', -1);
            }

            if (!partial) {
                return;
            }

            bindViewedEvents();
        }

        function applyInsightsToSearchParams(params = {}) {
            if (algoliaConfig.ccAnalytics.enabled) {
                params.clickAnalytics = true;
            }

            if (algoliaConfig.personalization.enabled) {
                params.enablePersonalization = true;
                params.userToken = determineUserToken();
            }

            return params;
        }


        function addSearchParameters() {
            if (window.hasAddedParameters) {
                return;
            }
            algolia.registerHook('beforeWidgetInitialization', function (allWidgetConfiguration) {
                allWidgetConfiguration.configure = applyInsightsToSearchParams(
                    allWidgetConfiguration.configure
                );
                return allWidgetConfiguration;
            });

            algolia.registerHook('afterAutocompleteProductSourceOptions', (options) => {
                return applyInsightsToSearchParams(options);
            });

            window.hasAddedParameters = true;
        }
    }

    function bindViewedEvents() {
        // viewed event is exclusive to personalization
        if (!window.algoliaConfig.personalization.enabled && !canTrack()) {
            return;
        }

        var viewConfig = window.algoliaConfig.personalization.viewedEvents.viewProduct;
        if (viewConfig.enabled) {
            if (document.body.classList.contains('catalog-product-view')) {
                const url = new URL(window.location.href);
                const objectId = url.searchParams.get("objectID");
                const indexName = url.searchParams.get("indexName");
                const queryID = url.searchParams.get("queryID");
                if (objectId) {
                    eventName = 'Product Viewed'
                    const viewData = {
                        eventName: viewConfig.eventName,
                        objectIDs: [objectId + ''],
                        index: indexName,
                        queryID: queryID
                    };
                    window.algoliaAnalytics.viewedObjectIDs(viewData);
                }
            }

        }
    }

    function canTrack() {
        return ((algoliaConfig.ccAnalytics.enabled
            || algoliaConfig.personalization.enabled) && window.algoliaConsent);
    }

    function buildInsightsEventData(element, eventName, objectId, indexName, position = null, queryId = null) {
        if (element.dataset.clicked === 'true' || !canTrack()) {
            return;
        }

        var eventData = {
            eventName: eventName,
            objectIDs: [objectId + ''],
            index: indexName
        };
        if (position) {
            eventData.positions = [parseInt(position)];
        }
        if (queryId) {
            eventData.queryID = queryId;
        }
        trackClick(eventData);
        element.dataset.clicked = true;
    }

    function trackClick(eventData) {
        if (eventData.queryID) {
            window.algoliaAnalytics.clickedObjectIDsAfterSearch(eventData);
        } else {
            window.algoliaAnalytics.clickedObjectIDs(eventData);
        }
    }
</script>
<div x-data="initPreorderAddToCartModal()" x-bind="eventListeners" x-cloak>
    <div x-transition:enter="transition ease-out duration-300"
         x-transition:enter-start="opacity-0"
         x-transition:enter-end="opacity-100"
         x-transition:leave="transition ease-in duration-300"
         x-transition:leave-start="opacity-100"
         x-transition:leave-end="opacity-0"
         x-show="isModalOpen"
         class="fixed z-50 top-0 left-0 w-full h-full bg-secondary/[.5] flex justify-center items-center"
         @private-content-loaded.window="receiveCustomerData($event.detail.data)">

        <div
            @click.outside="closeModal()"
            class="relative w-full mx-6 max-w-[608px] bg-primary px-6 py-8">
            <div @click="closeModal()"
                 class="absolute right-4 top-4 h-6 w-6 cursor-pointer">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="h-6 w-6" role="img">
<path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M12 12.7071L17.3033 18.0104L18.0104 17.3033L12.7071 12L18.0104 6.6967L17.3033 5.98959L12 11.2929L6.69669 5.98959L5.98959 6.69669L11.2929 12L5.98958 17.3033L6.69669 18.0104L12 12.7071Z" fill="#202020"/>
<title>x</title></svg>
            </div>

            <div class="w-full px-6 py-8 flex flex-col justify-center md:p-14 lg:px-14 lg:py-8">
                <h2 class="text-xl text-primary font-bold uppercase mb-4">
                    Are you sure?                </h2>
                <p class="m-0 text-base text-primary-lighter">
                    <template x-if="preorder">
                        <span>If you add this product you will only have preorder products in your cart. And you will loose your usual products, will you continue ?</span>
                    </template>
                    <template x-if="!preorder">
                        <span>If you add this product you will only have usual products in your cart. And you will loose your preorder products, will you continue ?</span>
                    </template>
                </p>

                <button class="btn btn-primary mt-10 w-full justify-center items-center h-12 cursor-pointer" type="submit" @click="submitForm()">
                    <span>Add this product</span>
                </button>

                <button class="btn btn-secondary mt-10 w-full justify-center items-center h-12 cursor-pointer" type="cancel" @click="cancelAddToCart()">
                    <span>Cancel</span>
                </button>

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<script>
    function initPreorderAddToCartModal() {
        return {
            cart: false,
            form: null,
            mobileloader: false,
            ctx: 'product',
            isModalOpen: false,
            preorder: false,
            eventListeners: {
                ['@add-to-cart-preorder-modal.window'](event) {
                    this.form = event.detail.form;
                    this.mobileloader = event.detail.mobileloader;
                    this.ctx = event.detail.ctx;

                    if (!this.shouldDisplayModal()) {
                        this.submitForm();
                    } else {
                        this.openModal();
                    }
                }
            },
            openModal() {
                this.isModalOpen = true;
                Alpine.store('bodyOverflow').disableOverflow();
            },
            closeModal() {
                if (!this.isModalOpen) {
                    return;
                }
                this.isModalOpen = false;
                this.cancelAddToCart();
                Alpine.store('bodyOverflow').enableOverflow();

            },
            cancelAddToCart() {
                window.dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('product-addtocart-complete'));
                this.closeModal();
            },
            shouldDisplayModal() {
                const formData = new FormData(this.form);
                this.preorder = formData.get('preorder') === 'true' || formData.get('preorder') === '1';

                window.dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('reload-customer-section-data'));

                if (!this.cart || !this.cart.items?.length || (this.preorder === !!(this.cart?.preorder))) {
                    return false;
                }
                return true;
            },
            receiveCustomerData(data) {
                if (data.cart) {
                    this.cart = data.cart;
                }
            },
            submitForm() {
                window.dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('add-to-cart-submit-' + this.ctx, {
                        detail:
                            {form: this.form, ctx: this.ctx, mobileloader: this.mobileloader}
                    }
                ));
                if (this.isModalOpen) {
                    this.closeModal();
                }
            }
        }
    }
</script>

    <script>
        window.ftldataLayer = window.ftldataLayer || [];

        function ftltag() {
            ftldataLayer.push(arguments);
        }

        function getFormattedSku(sku) {
            if (sku.includes('-')) {
                return sku.split('-')[0] ?? sku;
            }

            return sku;
        }

        ftltag('config', '593');

        const ftlScript = document.createElement('script');
        ftlScript.async = true;
        ftlScript.type = 'module';
        ftlScript.src = `https://recommender.fitle.com/ftltag.js?_=${new Date().getTime()}`;

        document.getElementsByTagName('head')[0].appendChild(ftlScript);
    </script>

    <script>
        window.addEventListener('product-addtocart-complete-callback', event => {
            if (!event.detail.productSku || !event.detail.productSize || !maisonHyva.getFitleTrackId()) {
                return;
            }

            ftltag(
                'event',
                'cart',
                {
                    product_id: getFormattedSku(event.detail.productSku),
                    size: event.detail.productSize
                }
            );
        });
    </script>
